<body>
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='ko'>부산은 한반도 남동쪽 해안가에 자리한
해안 도시입니다.
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='ko'>이웃 나라 수도인 베이징이나 도쿄까지는
단거리 비행으로,
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='ko'>서울에서는 고속 열차로 2시간 30분이면
갈 수 있는 거리에 있죠.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='ko'>우리나라에서 가장 큰 항구이자 두 번째로 큰 도시인 부산은
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='ko'>영남 지역의 들쭉날쭉한 해안선을 따라
펼쳐져 있으며
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='ko'>산으로 둘러싸인 아늑한 도시입니다.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='ko'>구석기 시대 사람들을 바위투성이 해안가로
몰려들게 한 조개류부터
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='ko'>싱싱한 해산물 천국인
자갈치 시장과
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='ko'>옛 조선 시대 선박부터
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='ko'>대한민국 경제 부흥의 주역인
조선소까지
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='ko'>부산은 언제나 바다와 함께해 왔죠.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='ko'>21세기에 접어들어서도
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='ko'>부산은 계속해서 성장을 거듭하였고
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='ko'>이제는 사람들이 열심히 일한 후
꿀 같은 휴식을 즐기면서
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='ko'>과거를 돌아보고
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='ko'>미래를 생각하는 안식처가 되었습니다.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='ko'>북적이는 항구에서는
부산의 활발한 경제 활동을 뒷받침하고
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='ko'>도시의 해변가는 아시아 전역에서 찾아온
여행객들의 발길을 사로잡죠.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='ko'>부산역에서 지하철로 40분 정도만 이동하면
주요 명소인 해운대를 만나실 수 있는데요.
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='ko'>이곳은 한국에서 가장 넓은 해변이자
가장 인기 많은 관광 명소예요.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='ko'>길게 펼쳐진 모래사장을 따라 동쪽으로 가면
달맞이 고개가 나옵니다.
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='ko'>옛날에는 시인들의 감수성을 자극하고
오늘날에는 커피 마니아들의
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='ko'>사랑을 듬뿍 받는 곳이에요.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='ko'>해운대 동쪽 끄트머리에 자리한
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='ko'>동백공원 산책길을 지나면 APEC 하우스를 마주하게 돼요.
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='ko'>이곳은 2005년도에 개최된 정상 회의 기간 동안
아태지역 지도자들이
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='ko'>부산의 수려한 경치를 조망했던 장소입니다.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='ko'>언제나 색다른 매력을 풍기는 부산의 바다는
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='ko'>취향에 맞는 다양한 액티비티를 즐기거나 경치를 감상할 수 있어요.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='ko'>반달 모양의
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='ko'>광안리 해수욕장에서
타월 한 장을 깔고 느긋하게 휴식을 취해 보세요.
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='ko'>부드러운 파도와
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='ko'>여유로운 분위기,
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='ko'>광안대교의 근사한 모습이 인상적일 거예요.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='ko'>활동적인 여행을 좋아하신다면
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='ko'>청사포 어촌 마을에서 배를 빌려 낚시를 떠나 보세요.
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='ko'>아니면 용호동 끄트머리에 있는
스카이워크를 걸으며
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='ko'>부산 앞바다의 오륙도가 선사하는 멋진 경치를
감상해 보세요.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='ko'>역사에 대해서도 알아보고 싶으신가요?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='ko'>그렇다면 기장으로 향해 보세요.
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='ko'>보기 드문 바닷가 사찰인
해동용궁사에서
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='ko'>간절하게 소원을 비는
경험을 해 보세요.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='ko'>오랜 역사를 자랑하는 영도대교를 건너
태종대공원으로 발걸음을 옮겨보세요.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='ko'>전해 내려오는 전설에 따르면
이 절벽은 신선과 선녀들이 내려와
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='ko'>멋진 경치를 즐기며 노닌 곳이기도 하며
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='ko'>29대 신라왕인 태종무열왕이 구름 사이로 화살을 쏘며
사냥을 즐긴 곳이기도 해요.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='ko'>오늘날에도 비록 신선은 아니지만
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='ko'>누구나 저 멀리 항구를 드나드는 화물선을 바라보며
마음의 위안을 찾기에
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='ko'>적합한 장소이지요.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='ko'>이렇게 차분한 분위기는 송도 해수욕장까지 이어집니다.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='ko'>바다 위에 떠 있는 산책길을 걸으며
경치를 즐겨보세요.
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='ko'>이 산책로의 곡선 형태는 바닷가 동굴에 사는
신화 속 용이 하늘로 솟아오르는 모양을 나타낸다고 해요.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='ko'>이제 다대포 해수욕장으로 가서
마음이 닿는 대로 거닐어 보세요.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='ko'>다대포 해수욕장은 우리나라에서 가장 긴 낙동강 하구에 있습니다.
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='ko'>이곳의 끝없이 펼쳐진 모래와 해무는 해안선을 흐릿하게 만들어
천국과 지상의 경계를 모호하게 만들죠.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='ko'>부산과 바다는 떼려야 뗄 수 없는 관계이지만
주변을 둘러싼 산들도
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='ko'>들려줄 이야기가 많습니다.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='ko'>항구 바로 위쪽으로
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='ko'>에스컬레이터를 타고 올라가면
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='ko'>용두산공원 정상에 도착하게 돼요.
이곳에는 16세기 해상 영웅인
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='ko'>이순신 장군의 동상이 세워져 있습니다.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='ko'>근처에 있는 천마산에서는
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='ko'>20분이면 오를 수 있는 전망대에 가 보세요.
&#39;다이나믹한 부산&#39;의 면모가
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='ko'>고스란히 눈 앞에 펼쳐질 거예요.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='ko'>북쪽에 자리한
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='ko'>부산에서 가장 높은 봉우리인 금강공원으로 가볼까요?
케이블카를 타고 5분 정도만 올라가면
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='ko'>도착할 수 있는 이곳에서는
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='ko'>매주 수천 명의 주민이 모여
금정산성을 둘러싼
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='ko'>숲속 산책로와 성벽길을 따라 
하이킹을 즐기는 모습이 펼쳐지죠.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='ko'>금강공원에는 범어사도 자리하고 있는데요.
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='ko'>이곳에서 수행했던 승려들은
16세기 임진왜란 때는 침략자들에 대항했고
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='ko'>20세기에 다시 한번 독립만세운동에 참여했어요.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='ko'>부산은 영웅들을 결코 잊지 않는 도시입니다.
근처 충렬사는
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='ko'>1592년 도시가 일본군에게 포위되었을 당시
자신의 목숨마저 기꺼이 희생했던
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='ko'>부산 애국자들의 영혼을
기리는 장소입니다.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='ko'>1950년, 부산은 또 한 번 포위되는 위험의 순간을 맞이했는데요.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='ko'>유엔기념공원에 들러
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='ko'>부산을 둘러싼 마지노선에서 북한군에 맞서 싸웠던
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='ko'>14만여 명의 군인들이 잠들어 있는
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='ko'>묘지를 방문해 보세요.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='ko'>부산은 한국전쟁 당시 함락되지 않은
몇 안 되는 도시 중 하나로
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='ko'>50만 명이 넘는 피난민들의 안전한 피난처 역할을 했어요.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='ko'>유엔평화기념관에도 들러보세요.
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='ko'>참전용사와 시민 희생자들을
기리고 있는 곳으로
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='ko'>전 세계적으로 진행 중인 여러 갈등으로 인해
고통받는 사람들에 대해 생각해 보는 시간이 될 거예요.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='ko'>부산은 피난민들로 인해 생겨난 고유의 문화가 많이 있습니다.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='ko'>전후 어려운 환경 속에서 탄생한 음식은
지금은 많은 사랑을 받는 훌륭한 요리가 되었으며
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='ko'>피난민 부부가 미군이 버리고 간 잡지를
주워다 팔던 골목길은
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='ko'>서점가로 바뀌었죠.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='ko'>그리고 새로운 정착민들이 기본 세간살이를 물물교환하던
자그마한 좌판들은
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='ko'>사람들의 발길이 끊이지 않는 우리나라 최대 규모의
전통 시장으로 성장하여
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='ko'>김치부터 운동화까지 없는 게 없는 곳이 되었어요.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='ko'>도시 변두리의 가파르고 척박한 언덕에
수백 채의 가주택이
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='ko'>들어서기도 전에
처음으로 항구 지역에 모여들었던 사람도 바로 이 피난민들이었습니다.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='ko'>쉬지 않고 열심히 일한 세월이 흐른 지금,
감천동 주민들은
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='ko'>창의적인 면모를 살려
길가와 벽면을
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='ko'>예술 작품으로 장식하여
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='ko'>자신들의 마을을
부산 최고의 관광 명소로 탈바꿈시켰죠.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='ko'>감천문화마을은 부산의
톡톡 튀는 개성 만점 문화와
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='ko'>경제적으로 활기찬 장소를 대표하고 있으며
이러한 기운은 이제 도시 전역으로 퍼져 나가고 있어요.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='ko'>세계 최고 수준의 박물관과
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='ko'>미술관,
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='ko'>축제에서 그 진가를 확인해 보세요.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='ko'>번화한 쇼핑 거리와
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='ko'>27만m²의 규모를 자랑하는 세계 최대 백화점을
둘러보세요.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='ko'>그리고 전 세계 미식가와 해산물 마니아들을 유혹하는
음식 냄새와 맛을 느껴보세요.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='ko'>환하게 빛나는 거리의 분위기를 느껴보세요.
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='ko'>매년 열리는 등불축제의 등불과도 같이
매일 밤 부산의 밤은 빛이 납니다.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='ko'>수 세기에 걸쳐 침입자들을 막아내고
수십 년의 고난과 투쟁의 세월을 이겨낸 부산은
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='ko'>마침내 부산만의 독특한 정체성을 가진
도시로 거듭나게 되었습니다.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='ko'>오늘날 부산은 과거와 미래를 서로 연결하여
아주 새로운 오늘을 만들어주는 완벽한 다리가 되어주고 있어요.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='ko'>오감은 물론 영혼까지 만족시키는
부산으로 여행을 떠나 보세요.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='ko'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='nl'>De stad Busan ligt aan de zuidoostelijke kust
van het Koreaanse schiereiland,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='nl'>een korte vlucht vanuit Aziatische hoofdsteden
zoals Peking en Tokio
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='nl'>en een ritje van tweeënhalf uur met
de hogesnelheidstrein vanuit Seoel.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='nl'>De grootste haven en op één na grootste stad
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='nl'>van Zuid-Korea spreidt zich uit over
de rotsachtige kustlijn van de regio Yeongnam
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='nl'>en verrijst daarachter in een zee van bergen.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='nl'>Van de schaaldieren die verzamelaars
in de oude steentijd naar de woeste kust lokte
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='nl'>tot de eindeloze aanbiedingen op de
Jagalchi Fish Market …
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='nl'>Van de oude Joseonschepen
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='nl'>tot de scheepswerven die het Zuid-Koreaanse
economische wonder hebben aangedreven,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='nl'>Busan is voor altijd met de oceaan verbonden.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='nl'>Terwijl de wereld door de 21e eeuw stoomt,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='nl'>blijft Busan zich ontwikkelen
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='nl'>tot een havenstad waar hardwerkende Koreanen
kunnen ontspannen,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='nl'>op het verleden kunnen reflecteren
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='nl'>en een blik in de toekomst kunnen werpen.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='nl'>Hoewel het de bruisende haven is
die de economische welvaart van Busan aandrijft,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='nl'>trekken de stranden van de stad
steeds meer reizigers vanuit heel Azië.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='nl'>Slechts een metrorit van 40 minuten vanaf Station Busan
ligt de beroemdste attractie van de stad:
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='nl'>het strand Haeundae, de grootste en
populairste badplaats van Zuid-Korea.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='nl'>Volg de lange zandstrook richting het oosten,
naar de Dalmaji-heuvel,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='nl'>een uitkijkpunt geprezen door de
rondtrekkende dichters van vroeger
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='nl'>en de koffieliefhebbers van nu.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='nl'>Als je aan de oostelijke rand van Haeundae bent,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='nl'>volg je de paden door het Dongbaek-park naar het APEC House,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='nl'>waar leiders uit Azië en het Pacifische gebied van een aantal
van de meest gewaardeerde uitzichten van Busan genoten
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='nl'>tijdens hun conferentie in 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='nl'>De altijd veranderende kustlijn van Busan biedt
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='nl'>een landschap en activiteiten voor elk humeur.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='nl'>Voor volledige ontspanning
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='nl'>leg je je handdoek op
het halvemaanvormige strand Gwangalli
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='nl'>en geniet je van het kalme water,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='nl'>de ontspannen sfeer
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='nl'>en het uitzicht op de Gwangan-brug.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='nl'>Als je op zoek bent naar avontuur,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='nl'>kun je mee met een charter vanuit het visstadje Cheongsapo.
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='nl'>Of zet een paar stappen op de skywalk aan het einde
van het schiereiland Yongho-Dong
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='nl'>en neem het uitzicht op de Oryukdo-eilanden
net van de kust in je op.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='nl'>Op zoek naar een beetje verlichting?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='nl'>Ga naar Gijang
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='nl'>en doe een wens
bij de Haedong Yonggungsa-tempel,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='nl'>een van de weinige Koreaanse boeddhistische tempels
die aan zee zijn gebouwd.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='nl'>Steek de historische Yeongdodaegyo-brug over
en ga naar het Taejongdae-park.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='nl'>Volgens de legendes waren het
deze kliffen
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='nl'>waar goden en godinnen ooit kwamen om te ontspannen
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='nl'>en waar de 29e koning van Silla in zijn vrije tijd
pijlen in voorbij komende wolken schoot.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='nl'>Voor de stervelingen van vandaag
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='nl'>is het park de ideale plek
om het rustig aan te doen
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='nl'>terwijl vrachtschepen naar verre havens varen.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='nl'>De meditatieve sfeer gaat verder op het strand Songdo.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='nl'>Wandel boven het golvende water op
het verhoogde voetpad,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='nl'>dat met zijn bochten lijkt op een mythische draak
die vanuit zijn nest aan de kust uitvliegt.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='nl'>Laat je gedachten de vrije loop en je kinderen
lekker spelen aan het strand Dadaepo.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='nl'>Hier aan de monding van Zuid-Korea’s langste rivier
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='nl'>kun je door het eindeloze zand en de zeemist haast
het verschil tussen hemel en aarde niet meer zien.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='nl'>Hoewel de geschiedenis van Busan steeds
door de zee is gevormd,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='nl'>staat de stad net zo bekend om zijn bergen.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='nl'>Net boven de haven kun je
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='nl'>met de roltrap naar de top van het Yongdusan-park
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='nl'>en het uitzicht delen met het standbeeld
van de 16e-eeuwse zeeheld
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='nl'>admiraal Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='nl'>Op de Cheonma-berg vlak bij
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='nl'>kom je met een wandeling van 20 minuten
op het uitkijkplatform waar ‘dynamisch Busan’
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='nl'>zich voor je uitspreidt.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='nl'>In het noorden van de stad
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='nl'>ben je met de kabelbaan binnen 5 minuten
in het Geumjeong-park,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='nl'>waar je het hoogste punt van Busan vindt.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='nl'>Sluit je aan bij de duizenden inwoners
die hier elk weekend wandelen
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='nl'>om de bospaden en de muren van 
het kasteel Geumjeongsanseong te verkennen.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='nl'>In het park staat ook de Beomeosa-tempel,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='nl'>waarvan de krijgsmonniken in de 16e eeuw
en later in de 20e eeuw
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='nl'>indringers wisten te verslaan.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='nl'>Busan vergeet zijn helden nooit
en bij de Chungnyeolsa-tempel in de buurt
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='nl'>kun je stilstaan bij de herinnering aan de patriotten
van Busan, die hun leven hebben gegeven
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='nl'>toen de stad in 1592 door Japanse troepen
werd belegerd.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='nl'>In 1950 werd Busan opnieuw belegerd.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='nl'>Bij de Erebegraafplaats Tanggok kun je
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='nl'>de graven bezoeken van een aantal van de 140.000 troepen
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='nl'>die de laatste verdedigingslinie om Busan vormden
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='nl'>toen ze tegen troepen van Noord-Koreaanse soldaten vochten.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='nl'>Busan was een van de weinige zuidelijke steden die tijdens
de Koreaanse Oorlog niet is gevallen, waardoor het 
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='nl'>voor ruim een half miljoen vluchtelingen een veilige haven werd.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='nl'>In de United Nations Peace Memorial Hall
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='nl'>worden de offers herdacht die zowel de krijgsmachten
als de burgers hebben gebracht.
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='nl'>Ook worden de lijdensverhalen van voortdurende
conflicten over de hele wereld herdacht.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='nl'>Busan heeft zijn veerkrachtige vluchtelingen veel te danken.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='nl'>Gerechten die zijn ontstaan in de moeilijke na-oorlogse tijd
zijn geperfectioneerd tot culinaire meesterwerken.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='nl'>Een steegje waar een vluchtelingenkoppel tijdschriften
verkocht die waren weggedaan door Amerikaanse soldaten,
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='nl'>is uitgegroeid tot een hele straat vol met boekenwinkels.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='nl'>En een paar bescheiden kraampjes waar de nieuwkomers
om de basisbenodigdheden handelden
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='nl'>groeiden uit tot de grootste en populairste
traditionele markt van Korea,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='nl'>waar alles, van kimchi tot sneakers, wordt verkocht.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='nl'>Eerst vulden de vluchtelingen de stadsdelen
aan de haven
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='nl'>en daarna bouwden ze honderden geïmproviseerde huizen
op de steile, kale heuvels om de stad.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='nl'>Na jaren keihard te hebben
gewerkt,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='nl'>hebben de inwoners van Gamcheon
hun creatieve kant omarmd.
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='nl'>Ze hebben hun straten en muren versierd met kunstwerken
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='nl'>die deze buurt hebben getransformeerd
tot een van de grootste bezienswaardigheden van de stad.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='nl'>De transformatie van Gamcheon staat symbool voor
de nieuwe creatieve, 
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='nl'>culturele en ondernemende sfeer
die overal in de stad is gaan bloeien.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='nl'>Bewonder deze sfeer in zijn uitstekende musea,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='nl'>… galeries,
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='nl'>… en festivals.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='nl'>Je hoort het in het vrolijke bruisen van de winkelstraten
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='nl'>en door de ruim 275 duizend vierkante meter
van het grootste warenhuis ter wereld.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='nl'>Ruik het, proef het, in een keuken die fijnproevers
en visliefhebbers van over de hele wereld lokt.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='nl'>En voel hoe het licht elke avond losbarst in de stad,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='nl'>net als tijdens het jaarlijkse
lantaarnfeest.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='nl'>Na jarenlang de vijand buiten de deur te hebben gehouden
en decennia van tegenspoed en keihard zwoegen,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='nl'>kan deze uitgelaten havenstad eindelijk
zichzelf zijn.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='nl'>Het Busan van nu is een brug, die het verleden
en de toekomst in een erg speciaal heden verbindt.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='nl'>Welkom in Busan, een feest voor de zintuigen
en de ziel.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='nl'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='no'>Byen Busan ligger på Koreahalvøyas
sør-østlige kystlinje,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='no'>kun en kort flytur unna asiatiske hovedsteder som
Beijing og Tokyo,
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='no'>og to og en halv time
med høyhastighetstog fra Seoul.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='no'>Sør-Koreas største havn og nest største by
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='no'>sprer seg langs den taggete kystlinjen
til regionen Yeongnam,
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='no'>og stiger opp som et hav av fjell på den andre siden.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='no'>Fra skalldyrene som trakk de paleoittiske
samlerne til den taggete kysten,
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='no'>til det uendelige utvalget på
Jagalchi fiskemarked ...
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='no'>Og med de gamle Joseon-skipene
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='no'>og verftene som bidrog til
Sør-Koreas enorme økonomiske vekst,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='no'>har Busan alltid vært tett knyttet til havet.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='no'>Og mens verden raser videre inn i det 21. århundre,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='no'>utvikler Busan seg videre
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='no'>til å bli et sted hvor hardtarbeidende koreanere kan
slå ut håret,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='no'>reflektere over fortiden
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='no'>og se inn i fremtiden.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='no'>Mens den livlige havnen er fundamentet for Busans
økonomiske livskraft,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='no'>er det strendene som i stadig økende grad
lokker til seg reisende fra hele Asia.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='no'>40 minutter med t-bane fra Busan stasjon
ligger byens hovedattraksjon,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='no'>Haeundae strand – Sør-Koreas største og
mest populære strand.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='no'>Følg de lange sandstrekkene østover til
Dalmaji-åsen,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='no'>et utkikkspunkt som har blitt nytt av vandrende poeter
i fortiden,
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='no'>og som beundres av kaffeelskere i dag.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='no'>Når du er på østsiden av Haeundae,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='no'>kan du følge veien gjennom Dongbaek park til APEC-huset.
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='no'>Her kunne ledere fra Asia og Stillehavet nyte noen
av Busans flotteste utsikter
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='no'>under konferansen i 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='no'>Busans varierte kystlinje har landskap
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='no'>og aktiviteter for alle humør.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='no'>For maksimal avslapning
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='no'>kan du brette ut håndkleet på den halvmåneformede
Gwangalli strand
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='no'>og nyte det behagelige vannet,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='no'>den rolige stemningen
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='no'>og utsikten til broen Gwangandaegyo.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='no'>Dersom du er ute etter et eventyr,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='no'>kan du bli med på en tur i fiskerlandsbyen Cheongsapo.
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='no'>Du kan også stige ut på skywalken på enden av
halvøya Yongho-Dong
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='no'>og betrakte utsikten over Oryukdo-øyene
like utenfor kysten.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='no'>Klar for å få dypere innsikt?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='no'>Dra til Gijang
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='no'>og ønsk deg noe
i Haedong Yonggungsa-tempelet,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='no'>et av de få buddhisttemplene i Korea
som ligger ved havet.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='no'>Kryss den historiske Yeongdodaegyo-broen og dra
til Taejongdae park.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='no'>Legenden sier at det
var disse klippene
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='no'>guder og gudinner kom til for å slappe av,
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='no'>og hvor den 29. kongen av Silla tilbrakte
ferien sin ved å skyte piler på skyene som gled forbi.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='no'>For dagens dødelige
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='no'>er parken det perfekte stedet for
å koble av
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='no'>og se på lasteskipene som drar avgårde.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='no'>Songdo strand kan by på mer meditativ stemning.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='no'>Gå over det virvlende vannet
på gangbroen
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='no'>som minner om en mytisk drage som
flyr avgårde fra hiet sitt på kysten.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='no'>La tankene fly og barna løpe
fritt på Dadaepo strand.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='no'>Her, ved munnen av Sør-Koreas lengste elv,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='no'>visker den endeløse sanden og havet
ut linjene mellom himmel og jord.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='no'>Busans historie har kontinuerlig blitt
formet av havet,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='no'>men byen er i like stor grad preget av fjellene sine.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='no'>Like over havnen
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='no'>kan du ta rulletrapp til toppen av Yongdusan-parken
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='no'>og nyte den samme utsikten som statuen av
sjøhelten fra 1500-tallet,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='no'>Admiral Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='no'>På fjellet Cheonma som ligger i nærheten
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='no'>kan du ta en 20 minutters gåtur til
utkikksplatået og se «dynamiske Busan»
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='no'>strekke seg ut foran deg.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='no'>Nord i byen
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='no'>kan du ta en fem minutters tur med taubane
til Geumgang-parken,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='no'>hvor du finner Busans høyeste topp.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='no'>Hit drar tusenvis av lokale på tur
hver helg
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='no'>for å utforske skogsstiene og veggene 
til Geumgang-festningen.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='no'>I parken finner du også Beomeosa-tempelet,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='no'>der krigsmunker nedkjempet inntrengere
først på 1500-tallet,
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='no'>og deretter på 1900-tallet.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='no'>Busan glemmer aldri heltene sine, og på
Chungnyeolsa-tempelet i nærheten
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='no'>kan du vise din respekt til Busans
patrioter som ofret livene sine
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='no'>da byen deres ble beleiret av japanske tropper
i 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='no'>I 1950 ble Busan beleiret nok en gang.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='no'>På FNs minnegravlund
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='no'>kan du besøke gravene til noen av de 140 000 soldatene
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='no'>som formet en siste fortvilet forsvarslinje rundt Busan,
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='no'>som kjempet mot nord-koreanske soldater.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='no'>Busan var en av de få byene i sør
som ikke falt under Koreakrigen,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='no'>og byen ble en trygg havn for over en halv million flyktninger.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='no'>På FNs fredsminnesenter
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='no'>blir ofringer fra både militære og sivile
husket,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='no'>i likhet med lidelsene fra pågående
konflikter over hele verden.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='no'>Busan skylder mye til sine utholdende flyktninger.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='no'>Retter som oppstod under trange kår etter krigen har blitt
videreutviklet til kulinariske mesterverk.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='no'>En bakgate hvor et flyktningpar solgte magasiner
som hadde blitt kastet av amerikanske soldater,
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='no'>vokste til en hel gate full av bokhandlere.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='no'>Og noen få enkle boder hvor de nyankomne
omsatte det aller mest nødvendige,
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='no'>er nå et av Koreas største og høyest elskede
tradisjonelle markeder,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='no'>hvor det selges alt fra Kimchi til joggesko.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='no'>Busans flyktninger fylte først
havneområdene,
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='no'>før de bygget hundrevis av provisoriske boliger
på de bratte, ufruktbare åsene rundt byen.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='no'>Etter å ha arbeidet som helter
i årevis,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='no'>har innbyggerne i Gamcheon omfavnet sine
kreative sider
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='no'>ved å utsmykke gatene og veggene sine med kunst,
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='no'>noe som har forvandlet nabolaget deres
til en av byens mest populære turistattraksjoner.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='no'>Gamcheons forvandling symboliserer Busans
nyvinnende kreative,
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='no'>kulturelle og oppfinnsomme energi som
har blomstret over hele byen.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='no'>Nyt fruktene av den kreative energien i museer,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='no'>gallerier
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='no'>og festivaler i verdensklasse.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='no'>Hør den i den muntre travelheten i handlegatene
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='no'>og i de nesten 280 000 kvadratmeterne
til verdens største varemagasin.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='no'>Lukt den og smak den i et kjøkken som elskes
av foodies og sjømatelskere fra hele verden.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='no'>Og føl den når byen glitrer i lys hver kveld,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='no'>akkurat som under den årlige
Lanternefesten i byen.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='no'>Etter århundrer med å stenge fiendene ute,
og tiår med trange kår og hart arbeid,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='no'>har denne lystige havnebyen blitt
noe helt særegent.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='no'>I dag er Busan en bro som knytter
fortiden og fremtiden sammen til noe helt spesielt.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='no'>Velkommen til Busan, en fest for alle sansene
og for sjelen.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='no'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='da'>Byen Busan befinder sig på den sydøstlige kystlinje
på den koreanske halvø,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='da'>kun en kort flyrejse fra asiatiske hovedstader som
Beijing og Tokyo
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='da'>og en tur på 2,5 time
med hurtigtoget til Seoul.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='da'>Sydkoreas største havn og anden største by
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='da'>breder sig langs den ujævne kystlinje
af Yeongnam-regionen
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='da'>og stiger op i havets horisont som bjerge.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='da'>Lige fra skaldyr, som lokkede samlere
fra den tidlige stenalder til,
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='da'>til de uendelige tilbud
på Jagalchis fiskemarked...
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='da'>Fra de gamle skibe fra Joseon-dynastien,
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='da'>til skibsværfterne, som succesfuldt
drev den sydkoreanske økonomi...
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='da'>Busan har i sandhed altid været forbundet med havet.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='da'>I en verden, der fortsat lever videre i det 21. århundrede med hastige skridt,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='da'>fortsætter Busan med at udvikle sig
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='da'>og er blevet et fristed for hårdtarbejdende koreanere,
som her kan slå håret ud
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='da'>og mindes fortiden,
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='da'>mens de kigger ud mod fremtiden.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='da'>Skønt det travle havneområde
er livskraften bag Busans økonomi,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='da'>er det byens strande, som gang på gang
tiltrækker rejsende fra hele Asien.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='da'>Du finder byens mest populære seværdighed,
Haeundae Strand, kun 40 minutter med metroen fra Busan Station,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='da'>som er Sydkoreas største
og mest eftertragtede tilholdssted.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='da'>Gå langs stranden mod øst
til Dalmaji Bakke,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='da'>et smukt landskab
elsket af fortidens omstrejfende poeter
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='da'>og nutidens kaffeentusiaster.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='da'>Mens du besøger den østlige del af Haeundae,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='da'>kan du passende kigge forbi Dongbaek Park og APEC Hus,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='da'>hvor asiatiske ledere nød godt af
Busans mest eftertragtede udsigter
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='da'>under topmødet i 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='da'>Busans forunderlige kystlinje byder på smukke landskaber
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='da'>og oplevelser til ethvert humør.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='da'>Trænger du til ren afslapning,
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='da'>kan du folde dit håndklæde ud
på Gwangalli Strand
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='da'>og nyde bølgernes brusen,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='da'>den afslappede atmosfære
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='da'>og udsigten til Diamond Bro.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='da'>Er du eventyrlysten,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='da'>kan du stige ombord på en fiskekutter i landsbyen Cheongsapo,
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='da'>eller du kan gå en tur
langs Yongho-Dong-halvøens skywalk
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='da'>og nyde udsigten
fra Oryukdo-øerne ud for kysten.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='da'>Har du brug for en lille opmuntring?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='da'>Tag til Gijang,
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='da'>og ønsk dig noget særligt
ved Haedong Yonggungsa Tempel,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='da'>der er et af de få buddhistiske templer i Korea,
som er bygget ved havet.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='da'>Kryds den historiske Yeongdodaegyo Bro,
og tag et smut forbi Taejongdae Park.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='da'>Det siges, at det var ved disse klipper,
guder og gudinder drog til
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='da'>for at slappe af og stedet,
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='da'>hvor den 29. konge af Silla brugte sin tid på
at skyde med bue og pile ud i horisonten.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='da'>I dag er parken perfekt til dem,
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='da'>som ønsker at geare ned og
og finde indre ro,
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='da'>mens skibene langsomt sejler forbi.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='da'>Den meditative atmosfære fortsætter ved Songdo Strand.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='da'>Gå på tværs af det hvirvlende vand
højt oppe på gangstien,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='da'>hvis form afbilder en mytisk drage
og flugter ud i de kystlige vinde.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='da'>Lad derefter tankerne og børnene
løbe frit på Dadaepo Strand.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='da'>Her ved udmundingen af Sydkoreas længste flod,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='da'>mødes det bløde sand og de milde havvinde
mellem himmel og jord.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='da'>Selvom Busans historie i høj grad
er præget af havet,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='da'>er byen i ligeså stor en grad defineret af dens bjerge.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='da'>Tag rulletrappen til bjergtoppen af Yongdusan Park
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='da'>som befinder sig over havnen,
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='da'>og nyd udsigten sammen med statuen
af den maritime helt fra det 16. århundrede,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='da'>Admiral Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='da'>Gå en tur på 20 minutter op til udkigsposten
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='da'>på det nærliggende bjerg Cheonma,
og beundr Busans dynamiske hverdag
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='da'>foran dine fødder.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='da'>I den nordlige del af byen,
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='da'>kan du tage kabelbanen og opleve Geumgang Park,
som ligger sig blot fem minutter væk,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='da'>og du befinder dig på Busans højeste punkt.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='da'>Gør som tusinder af de lokale,
og vandr derop hver weekend
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='da'>for at udforske skovens snoede stier 
og Geumgang Borg.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='da'>Parken er også hjemsted for Beomeosa Tempel,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='da'>hvis krigeriske munke kæmpede mod indtrængende fjender
i det 16. århundrede
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='da'>og igen i det 20. århundrede.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='da'>Busan glemmer ikke sine helte,
og i det nærliggende Chungnyeolsa Tempel
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='da'>kan du vise din respekt til Busans patrioters ånder,
som ofrede deres liv,
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='da'>dengang byen blev bestormet
af japanske tropper i 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='da'>I 1950 blev Busan igen belejret.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='da'>Ved FN’s Mindesmærkegravplads
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='da'>kan du opleve gravsteder fra nogle af de 140.000 tropper,
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='da'>der danner en grøft omkring Busan,
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='da'>og som kæmpede mod nordkoreanske soldater.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='da'>Busan var en af de få sydlandske byer,
som ikke faldt under den Koreakrigen,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='da'>og blev da et tilflugtssted for over en halv million flygtninge.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='da'>Ved FN’s Peace Memorial Hall
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='da'>mindes både krigere og civile
samt de sørgelige historier
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='da'>fra vedvarende konflikter
rundt om i verden.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='da'>Busan står i gæld til dens modstandsdygtige flygtninge.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='da'>Retter opfundet efter krigens strabadser
er blevet udviklet til kulinariske mesterværker.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='da'>En smøge, som dengang var et sted, hvor flygtningepar solgte magasiner,
der blev frasorteret af amerikanske soldater,
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='da'>står i dag som en gade fuld af diverse boghandlere.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='da'>Og et par daværende boder,
hvor ydmyge tilflyttere forhandlede basale varer,
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='da'>er nu et af Koreas største
og mest attraktive traditionelle markeder,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='da'>hvor du finder alt fra Kimchi til kondisko.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='da'>Busans flygtninge strømmede først til havneområderne,
før de byggede hundredvis af midlertidige huse
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='da'>på de ufrugtbare bakker
omkring selve byen.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='da'>Efter flere års hårdt arbejde
er indbyggerne i Gamcheon
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='da'>begyndt at udfolde deres kreative side
og udsmykker gader og mure
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='da'>med kunst, som har forvandlet kvarteret
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='da'>og er i dag en af byens mest
populære seværdigheder blandt turister.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='da'>Gamcheons makeover symboliserer Busans
kreative, kulturelle
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='da'>og nyskabende talenter,
som blomstrer over hele byen.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='da'>Du kan se disse kreative værker i verdensklasse på museer,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='da'>...i gallerier
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='da'>...og på festivaller.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='da'>Oplev den glade stemning i shoppinggaderne
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='da'>og på tværs af det store indkøbscenter,
som er mere end 200.000 kvm stort.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='da'>Nyd duften, og smag på det i et køkken, som lokker foodies
og folk, som elsker alt godt fra havet, til fra hele verden.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='da'>Og oplev det, idet byen stråler hver nat,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='da'>ligesom fra lanterne
fra dens årlige festival.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='da'>Efter århundreder, hvor man har forsøgt at holde fjender væk,
og årtier med trængsler og hårdt arbejde
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='da'>er denne by endelig
blevet helt sin egen.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='da'>I dag er Busan en bro, som forbinder
fortiden og fremtiden sammen i nutiden.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='da'>Velkommen til Busan – en fest for alle sanser
og for sjælen.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='da'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='de'>Die Stadt Busan liegt an der Südostküste
der Koreanischen Halbinsel. Sie ist nur
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='de'>einen kurzen Flug von asiatischen Hauptstädten
wie Peking und Tokio und 2,5 Stunden
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='de'>mit dem Hochgeschwindigkeitszug
von Seoul entfernt.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='de'>Südkoreas größter Hafen und zweitgrößte Stadt
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='de'>erstreckt sich entlang der felsigen Küste
der Region Yeongnam und ist
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='de'>von einer Bergkette umgeben.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='de'>Von den Meeresfrüchten, die altsteinzeitliche
Sammler an die Felsenküsten lockten,
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='de'>bis hin zum reichhaltigen Angebot des
Jagalchi-Fischmarkts,
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='de'>von den alten Schiffen des Königreichs Joseon
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='de'>bis hin zum Hafen, der maßgeblich zu
Südkoreas Wirtschaftswunder beitrug,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='de'>war Busan schon immer untrennbar mit dem Meer verbunden.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='de'>Auch im 21. Jahrhundert entwickelt sich
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='de'>Busan stetig weiter und ist heute ein Ort,
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='de'>an dem die Koreaner die Früchte
ihrer harten Arbeit ernten,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='de'>sich auf ihre Vergangenheit besinnen
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='de'>und in die Zukunft schauen können.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='de'>Obwohl der Hafen Busans zum
wirtschaftlichen Erfolg beiträgt,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='de'>sind es doch die Strände der Stadt, die
immer mehr Urlauber aus ganz Asien anziehen.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='de'>Nur 40 Minuten mit der U-Bahn vom
Bahnhof Busan entfernt ist die Hauptattraktion:
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='de'>der Strand von Haeundae, Südkoreas größter
und beliebtester Strand.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='de'>Östlich des langen Sandstrands liegt
die Anhöhe Dalmaji Hill, deren
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='de'>Panoramablick seit jeher Dichter 
und Wanderer anzog –
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='de'>und heute auch Kaffeeliebhaber.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='de'>Am östlichen Ende von Haeundae schlendert
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='de'>man durch den Dongbaek-Park zum APEC House,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='de'>wo 2005 die Asiatisch-Pazifische
Wirtschaftsgemeinschaft zusammentraf, um
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='de'>vor beeindruckender Kulisse zu tagen.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='de'>Die vielfältigen Küstenabschnitte von Busan bieten
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='de'>Aussichten und Aktivitäten für jeden Geschmack.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='de'>Um auszuspannen,
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='de'>können Sie Ihr Handtuch am halbmondförmigen
Strand von Gwangalli ausrollen
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='de'>und das ruhige Meer,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='de'>die relaxte Stimmung und die
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='de'>Aussicht auf die Diamond Bridge genießen.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='de'>Abenteuerlustige können im Fischerdorf
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='de'>Cheongsapo eine Bootsfahrt unternehmen.
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='de'>Oder Sie erklimmen den Skywalk am Ende
der Halbinsel Yongho-Dong und
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='de'>genießen den Blick auf die Inselgruppe Oryukdo
direkt vor der Küste.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='de'>Sind Sie auf der Suche nach Erleuchtung?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='de'>Dann besichtigen Sie Gijang und
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='de'>bitten Sie im Tempel Haedong Yonggungsa
um einen Wunsch.
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='de'>Er ist einer der wenigen buddhistischen Tempel
in Korea, die direkt am Meer erbaut wurden.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='de'>Überqueren Sie die alte Yeongdodaegyo-Klappbrücke,
um zum Taejongdae-Park zu gelangen.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='de'>Der Legende nach kamen die Göttinnen und Götter
einst an diese Klippen,
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='de'>um sich zu entspannen.
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='de'>Der 29. König von Silla schoss von hier aus
zum Vergnügen Pfeile in die vorbeiziehenden Wolken.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='de'>Für die Sterblichen von heute ist der Park
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='de'>ideal, um Körper und Geist auszuruhen
und dabei den Frachtschiffen zuzusehen,
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='de'>wie sie ferne Häfen ansteuern.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='de'>Einen fast meditativen Zustand erreicht man auch
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='de'>am Strand von Songdo, dessen Strandpromenade
über dem Wasser schwebt.
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='de'>Die geschwungene Form erinnert an einen Drachen,
der zum Flug ansetzt.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='de'>Lassen Sie anschließend Ihren Gedanken – und
Ihren Kindern – am Strand von Dadaepo freien Lauf.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='de'>Hier, an der Mündung des längsten Flusses
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='de'>von Südkorea, verschwimmen die Grenzen zwischen
Himmel und Erde.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='de'>Obwohl Busans Geschichte maßgeblich
vom Meer geprägt ist,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='de'>sind auch die Berge immer präsent.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='de'>Direkt über dem Hafen fährt
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='de'>eine Rolltreppe zur Spitze des Yongdusan-Parks.
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='de'>Hier steht die Statue des brillantesten
Militärstrategen aus dem 16. Jahrhundert,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='de'>Admiral Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='de'>Die Aussichtsplattform auf dem
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='de'>nahe gelegenen Berg Cheonma ist
zu Fuß in 20 Minuten erreicht und
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='de'>bietet einen tollen Blick auf Busan.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='de'>Im Norden der Stadt
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='de'>bringt Sie eine Seilbahn in fünf Minuten
zum Geumgang-Park,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='de'>wo sich der höchste Berg Busans befindet.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='de'>Tausende Einheimische wandern hier
jedes Wochenende auf den
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='de'>Waldwanderwegen und entlang der Mauern 
der Festung Geumgang.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='de'>Im Park befindet sich auch
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='de'>der Beomeosa-Tempel, dessen Kriegermönche
im 16. und 20. Jahrhundert
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='de'>Invasoren abwehrten.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='de'>Busan vergisst seine Helden nicht und im
nahe gelegenen Chungnyeolsa-Tempel
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='de'>wird der Patrioten gedacht,
die ihr Leben ließen, als die Stadt 1592
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='de'>von japanischen Truppen
belagert wurde.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='de'>1950 wurde Busan erneut belagert.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='de'>Auf dem UN Memorial Cemetery fanden
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='de'>viele der 140.000 Soldaten ihre letzte Ruhe,
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='de'>die eine schmale Verteidigungslinie gegen
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='de'>den nordkoreanischen Vormarsch schützten.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='de'>Busan war eine der wenigen Städte im Süden,
die im Koreakrieg nicht eingenommen wurde,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='de'>und gab so über einer halben Million Flüchtlinge Obdach.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='de'>In der UN Peace Memorial Hall
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='de'>wird an die Opfer erinnert, die Soldaten
und Zivilisten bringen mussten.
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='de'>Auch des Leids durch aktuelle Konflikte
auf der Erde wird gedacht.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='de'>Busan hat seinen zähen Flüchtlingen viel zu verdanken.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='de'>Gerichte, die aus der Not der Nachkriegszeit heraus entstanden,
wurden zu kulinarischen Meisterwerken perfektioniert.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='de'>Aus einer Gasse, in der Flüchtlinge Zeitschriften
verkauften, die amerikanische Soldaten wegwarfen,
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='de'>wurde eine ganze Straße voller Buchhandlungen.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='de'>Und aus einigen ärmlichen Ständen, wo die
Neuankömmlinge mit Waren des täglichen Bedarfs handelten,
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='de'>ist einer der größten und beliebtesten
traditionellen Märkte Koreas geworden,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='de'>auf dem es von Kimchi bis Turnschuhen alles gibt.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='de'>Die Flüchtlinge siedelten sich zunächst
rund um den Hafen an.
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='de'>Später entstanden Hunderte provisorische Häuser
an den Hängen der unwirtlichen Hausberge.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='de'>Nach Jahren harter und entbehrungsreicher Arbeit
haben die Einwohner von Gamcheon
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='de'>ihre kreative Seite entdeckt
und dekorieren ihre Straßen und Wände mit
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='de'>farbenfrohen Kunstwerken, die das Viertel
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='de'>zu einer der beliebtesten Touristenattraktionen
von Busan machen.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='de'>Gamcheons Imagewechsel symbolisiert die
neu entdeckte kreative, kulturelle
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='de'>und unternehmerische Energie,
die in ganz Busan zu spüren ist.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='de'>Diese Energie können Sie sehen:
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='de'>in den erstklassigen Museen,
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='de'>Galerien und Festivals.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='de'>Sie können sie hören im fröhlichen Trubel
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='de'>der Einkaufsstraßen und im
größten Shoppingcenter der Welt.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='de'>Riechen und schmecken Sie die Energie
in der koreanischen Küche, die weltweit begeistert.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='de'>Und spüren Sie sie, wenn Busan nachts
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='de'>in unendlich vielen Lichtern erstrahlt, genauso wie
beim jährlichen Laternenfest.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='de'>Nach jahrhundertelanger Abschottung vor Feinden
und Jahrzehnten harter Arbeit und Entbehrungen
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='de'>hat die lebendige Hafenstadt nun endlich
zu sich selbst gefunden.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='de'>Heute ist Busan eine Brücke, die die Vergangenheit
und die Zukunft zu einem ganz besonderen Jetzt verbindet.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='de'>Willkommen in Busan – einem Fest für alle Sinne
und für die Seele.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='de'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='vi'>Thành phố Busan tọa lạc trên bờ biển phía đông nam
Bán đảo Triều Tiên,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='vi'>cách thủ đô các nước châu Á như Bắc Kinh và Tokyo
chỉ một chặng bay ngắn
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='vi'>và cách Seoul 2,5 giờ
đi tàu siêu tốc.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='vi'>Cảng biển lớn nhất và cũng là thành phố lớn thứ hai Hàn Quốc
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='vi'>trải mình dọc theo đường bờ biển mấp mô thuộc
Khu vực Yeongnam,
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='vi'>vươn ra cả vùng núi phía xa.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='vi'>Từ bao loài sò ốc đã đưa chân người hái lượm thời Đồ đá Cũ
tới bờ biển trắc trở
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='vi'>đến bạt ngàn hàng hóa
của Chợ Cá Jagalchi,
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='vi'>…từ những con tàu cũ xưa thời Triều Tiên
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='vi'>đến các bến tàu đã góp phần
giúp kinh tế Hàn Quốc viết nên kỳ tích,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='vi'>Busan trọn kiếp gắn bó với đại dương.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='vi'>Khi cả thế giới mải miết chạy đua cùng thế kỷ 21,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='vi'>Busan vẫn vững bước trên con đường riêng,
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='vi'>trở thành thiên đường cho những người con cần mẫn xứ kim chi
được sống vô tư lự,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='vi'>trân trọng quá khứ,
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='vi'>ngóng chờ tương lai.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='vi'>Chẳng chịu kém bến cảng sầm uất đặt nền móng
cho tiềm lực kinh tế của Busan,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='vi'>những bãi biển trong thành phố
ngày càng thu hút du khách từ khắp châu Á.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='vi'>Và nổi bật nhất trong số ấy,
chỉ mất 40 phút đi tàu điện ngầm từ Ga Busan,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='vi'>là Bãi biển Haeundae không những lớn nhất
mà còn được yêu thích nhất Hàn Quốc.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='vi'>Phía đông dải cát dài,
Đồi Dalmaji
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='vi'>làm say lòng những thi sĩ phiêu lãng
thuở xưa
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='vi'>và cả bao người chuộng cà phê ngày nay.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='vi'>Cũng ở đầu phía đông Haeundae,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='vi'>đường to lối nhỏ vắt ngang Công viên Dongbaek, dẫn đến APEC House,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='vi'>nơi các nhà lãnh đạo châu Á và Thái Bình Dương
thưởng lãm những cảnh sắc nổi danh nhất Busan
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='vi'>trong hội nghị thượng đỉnh năm 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='vi'>Đường bờ biển đa dạng mà tấp nập trò vui của Busan
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='vi'>là thiên đường cho tất cả.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='vi'>Giây phút thư thái nhất
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='vi'>là khi ta nhẹ trải chiếc khăn mềm
trên Bãi biển Gwangalli hình bán nguyệt,
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='vi'>ngụp lặn giữa nước mát dịu êm,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='vi'>đắm chìm trong nhịp đời thư thái
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='vi'>và thảnh thơi ngắm Cầu Diamond.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='vi'>Ai muốn trải nghiệm chút phiêu lưu
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='vi'>chỉ cần đến làng chài Cheongsapo thuê tàu ra khơi,
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='vi'>mạnh dạn bước trên đường đi bộ trên cao
ở cuối Bán đảo Yongho-Dong
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='vi'>và mê đắm bức tranh Đảo Oryukdo
ngay ngoài khơi.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='vi'>Tìm ánh sáng cho tâm hồn lạc lối ư?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='vi'>Sao không đến huyện Gijang
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='vi'>và tỏ lời ước nguyện tại
Chùa Haedong Yonggungsa,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='vi'>một trong những ngôi chùa Phật giáo hiếm hoi tại Hàn Quốc
xây bên bờ đại dương.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='vi'>Bên kia Cầu Yeongdodaegyo lịch sử,
Công viên Taejongdae ấn tượng biết bao.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='vi'>Truyền thuyết kể rằng
những vách đá nơi ấy
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='vi'>từng đón bao thần tiên đến nghỉ chân
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='vi'>và cả vị vua đời thứ 29 nước Tân La tới lúc thư nhàn,
lấy trò bắn tên lên mây trời làm vui.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='vi'>Còn với trần thế hôm nay,
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='vi'>công viên là điểm hẹn tuyệt vời
để buông bỏ sầu lo, thả hồn theo
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='vi'>đoàn tàu chở hàng tới những bến cảng xa xôi.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='vi'>Bầu không khí an nhiên cũng bao phủ Bãi biển Songdo.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='vi'>Lối đi xây cao bắc ngang
vùng nước đang cuộn chảy
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='vi'>thấp thoáng những đường cong tái hiện cảnh
mãnh long trong truyền thuyết vút bay từ hang rồng ven biển.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='vi'>Đến Bãi biển Dadaepo, khi cha mẹ tranh thủ thư giãn
thì bọn trẻ chạy nhảy nô đùa khắp chốn.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='vi'>Chính đây, cửa con sông dài nhất Hàn Quốc,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='vi'>cát trải miên man và sương mù vùng biển
như xóa nhòa ranh giới giữa đất trời.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='vi'>Dẫu biết Busan xưa nay
chẳng tách rời biển cả,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='vi'>thế nhưng thành phố cũng in dấu núi non.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='vi'>Ngay phía trên bến cảng,
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='vi'>hệ thống thang máy chạy thẳng lên đỉnh Công viên Yongdusan,
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='vi'>đưa du khách đến ngắm bao cảnh đẹp
trải rộng trước bức tượng anh hùng hải quân thế kỷ 16,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='vi'>Đô đốc Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='vi'>Trên Núi Cheonma gần kề,
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='vi'>chỉ mất 20 phút thôi là ta sẽ tới đài quan sát,
để thấy “Busan năng động”
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='vi'>khoe mình trọn vẹn.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='vi'>Phía bắc thành phố,
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='vi'>xe cáp treo chỉ chạy khoảng năm phút
là tới Công viên Geumgang,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='vi'>nơi có đỉnh núi cao nhất Busan.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='vi'>Dân bản xứ đổ về đây dạo bộ mỗi cuối tuần
có tới hàng ngàn người,
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='vi'>những con đường rừng và tường thành 
thuộc Pháo đài Geumgang càng làm cảnh quan thêm kỳ vĩ.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='vi'>Chùa Beomeosa trong công viên từng có
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='vi'>các nhà sư chiến đấu chống quân xâm lược
trong thế kỷ 16
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='vi'>và sau đó là vào thế kỷ 20.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='vi'>Busan muôn đời ghi công các anh hùng,
Chùa Chungnyeolsa gần đó
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='vi'>mãi dành trọn niềm tôn kính cho hương hồn
những người con ái quốc của Busan đã hi sinh
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='vi'>khi thành phố quê hương bị quân Nhật bao vây
năm 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='vi'>Năm 1950, Busan lại một lần nữa rơi vào vòng vây hãm.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='vi'>Nghĩa trang Tưởng niệm Liên Hiệp Quốc
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='vi'>là nơi yên nghỉ của nhiều người trong 140.000 binh lính
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='vi'>từng quyết giữ tuyến phòng thủ cuối cùng quanh Busan,
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='vi'>chống trả lớp lớp quân Bắc Triều Tiên.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='vi'>Busan nằm trong số ít các thành phố phương nam
không bị nhấn chìm trong Chiến tranh Triều Tiên,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='vi'>trở thành chốn nương náu cho hơn nửa triệu dân tị nạn.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='vi'>Nhà Tưởng niệm Hòa Bình Liên Hiệp Quốc
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='vi'>như lời nhắc nhở nhức nhối về sự hy sinh
dẫu của binh lính hay thường dân,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='vi'>câu chuyện về sự thương đau mà các cuộc xung đột
vẫn đang gieo rắc trên toàn cầu.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='vi'>Có được Busan ngày nay là nhờ công lao của lớp người tị nạn kiên cường.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='vi'>Những món ăn bắt nguồn từ khốn khó thời hậu chiến
dần hoàn thiện thành kiệt tác ẩm thực.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='vi'>Hẻm nhỏ ngày xưa có cặp vợ chồng tị nạn bán tạp chí
mà lính Mỹ vứt bỏ
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='vi'>giờ đã thành con phố ngập tràn tiệm sách.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='vi'>Và mấy quầy hàng hiu hắt thuở trước mà dân mới đến
kinh doanh hàng tiêu dùng thường ngày
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='vi'>nay ghi tên mình trong những khu chợ truyền thống
lớn nhất, được yêu thích nhất Hàn Quốc,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='vi'>bán từ Kimchi đến giày sneaker.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='vi'>Dân tị nạn đến Busan lúc đầu tập trung
ở các khu vực ven bến cảng,
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='vi'>sau đó mới dựng xây hàng trăm ngôi nhà tạm
trên những đồi dốc cằn cỗi quanh thành phố.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='vi'>Sau bao năm bán mặt cho đất,
bán lưng cho trời,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='vi'>dân làng Gamcheon cũng dành tâm sức
sáng tạo.
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='vi'>Họ trang trí đường hẻm và tường bao bằng nghệ thuật,
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='vi'>biến ngôi làng thân thương
thành điểm du lịch hàng đầu thành phố.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='vi'>Sự đổi thay của Gamcheon tượng trưng cho
sức sáng tạo, bản sắc văn hóa
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='vi'>và tiềm năng kinh tế mới khai phá
đã đơm hoa kết trái khắp Busan.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='vi'>Sắc màu ấy rực rỡ trong những bảo tàng tầm cỡ thế giới,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='vi'>...phòng triển lãm
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='vi'>...và bao lễ hội.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='vi'>Thanh âm ấy vọng vang trong cái náo nhiệt vui tươi khắp những phố mua sắm
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='vi'>và trên diện tích 3 triệu foot vuông của
cửa hàng bách hóa lớn nhất thế giới.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='vi'>Hương vị ấy đậm đà trong những món ăn chinh phục
tín đồ ẩm thực và dân nghiền hải sản bốn phương.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='vi'>Và xúc cảm ấy chạm vào tim ta khi thành phố lên đèn,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='vi'>rạng rỡ tựa như lễ hội đèn lồng
hàng năm.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='vi'>Sau bao thế kỷ ngoan cường cầm chân kẻ thù
và bao thập kỷ nếm mật nằm gai,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='vi'>thành phố cảng mạnh mẽ cuối cùng
cũng tỏa hào quang riêng.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='vi'>Busan của hôm nay là nhịp cầu nối liền
quá khứ và tương lai với hiện tại đẹp đẽ vô ngần.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='vi'>Hãy đến với Busan, bữa đại tiệc cho mọi giác quan
và cho cả tâm hồn.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='vi'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='sv'>Staden Pusan ligger vid Koreahalvöns
södra kust,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='sv'>bara en kort flygresa från asiatiska huvudstäder som
Beijing och Tokyo,
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='sv'>och 2,5 timmars resa med snabbtåg
från Seoul.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='sv'>Sydkoreas största hamnstad och nästa största stad
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='sv'>breder ut sig längs Yeongnam-regionens
klippiga kustlinje,
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='sv'>och tornar upp sig i ett landskap som är omgivet av berg.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='sv'>Från skaldjur – som lockade samlare till dessa steniga
stränder under stenåldern –
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='sv'>till Jagalchis fiskmarknad
med ett utbud som aldrig sinar,
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='sv'>...från Joseons urgamla fartyg
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='sv'>till skeppsvarven som hjälpte Sydkoreas
ekonomi att blomstra;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='sv'>Pusan har alltid varit förknippat med havet.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='sv'>I takt med att civilisationen skrider längre in i 2000-talet,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='sv'>fortsätter Pusan att utvecklas till
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='sv'>en fristad där hårt arbetande koreaner kan
koppla av,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='sv'>reflektera över det förgångna
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='sv'>och blicka in i framtiden.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='sv'>Samtidigt som denna livliga hamnstad
är en grundpelare för landets ekonomi,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='sv'>är det Pusans stränder som lockar allt fler
resenärer hit från hela Asien.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='sv'>Bara en 40 minuters resa med tunnelbana från Pusan station
ligger stadens populäraste sevärdhet,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='sv'>Haeundae Beach – Sydkoreas största och
mest omtyckta badstrand.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='sv'>Följ de långa sanddynerna österut mot
Dalmaji Hill,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='sv'>en utsiktsplats älskad av gårdagens
poeter och
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='sv'>nutidens kaffe-entusiaster.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='sv'>När du är vid Haeundaes östra ände
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='sv'>kan du passa på att ta en promenad genom Dongbaek Park till APEC House,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='sv'>där politiska ledare från Asien och Stillahavsområdet
beundrade några av Pusans favoritvyer
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='sv'>under toppmötet 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='sv'>Pusans variationsrika kust erbjuder natur
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='sv'>och aktiviteter som passar alla.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='sv'>Om du är ute efter total avslappning
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='sv'>kan du rulla ut badhandduken på den halvmåneformade
Gwangalli Beach.
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='sv'>Här får du njuta av lugna vatten,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='sv'>en avkopplande atmosfär och utsikten över
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='sv'>Diamond Bridge.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='sv'>Om du är på jakt efter äventyr,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='sv'>ta en charterutflykt till Cheongsapos fiskeby
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='sv'>eller kliv ut på Oryukdo Skywalk på änden av
halvön i Yongho-Dong
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='sv'>och beskåda utsikten över Oryukdo-öarna
som ligger precis utanför kusten.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='sv'>Söker du ett spirituellt lugn?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='sv'>Bege dig till Gijang
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='sv'>och önska dig något vid Haedong Yonggungsa-
templet,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='sv'>ett av de få buddhistiska tempel i Korea som byggdes
vid havet.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='sv'>Korsa den historiska Yeongdodaegyobron och
promenera vidare mot Taejongdae Park.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='sv'>Det var hit, enligt
legenden,
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='sv'>som gudar och gudinnor kom för att koppla av,
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='sv'>och även hit som den 29:e kungen av Silla kom på sin fritid
för att skjuta iväg pilar mot de förbiseglande molnen.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='sv'>För dagens vanliga dödliga
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='sv'>är parken den perfekta platsen för att
sjunka ner i lugna tankar
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='sv'>under tiden som fraktfartyg glider iväg mot avlägsna hamnar.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='sv'>Sinnesron dröjer sig kvar på Songdo Beach.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='sv'>Vandra ut över det skummande havet utmed det högt belägna
vandringsstråket,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='sv'>vars kurvor föreställer en mytomspunnen drake
som är på väg att flyga upp från sin kustlya.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='sv'>Dröm dig sedan bort och låt barnen leka
fritt på Dadaepo Beach.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='sv'>Här, vid mynningen av Sydkoreas längsta flod,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='sv'>suddar de oändliga stränderna och havsdimmorna ut skiljelinjen
mellan himmel och jord.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='sv'>Pusans historia har ständigt
formats av havet,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='sv'>men staden har formats lika mycket av sina berg.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='sv'>Precis ovanför hamnen
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='sv'>kan du ta rulltrappan mot toppen av Yongdusan Park,
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='sv'>och beundra utsikten tillsammans med statyn av
amiralen Yi Sun Sin,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='sv'>en hjälte i den koreanska flottan på 1500-talet.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='sv'>På berget Cheonmasan i närheten
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='sv'>kan du ta en 20 minuters vandringstur upp till
utsiktsplatsen för att se ”dynamiska Pusan”
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='sv'>breda ut sig framför dig.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='sv'>I stadens norra del
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='sv'>kan du ta en fem minuters åktur med linbana
till Geumgang Park,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='sv'>hemvisten för Pusans högsta bergstopp.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='sv'>Följ fotspåren av alla tusentals lokalbor som kommer hit
för att vandra på helgen,
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='sv'>och utforska skogsstigarna och 
murarna av Geumgangs fästning.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='sv'>I parken hittar du också Beomeosa-templet,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='sv'>vars krigarmunkar stred för att värja sig mot inkräktare
på 1500-talet,
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='sv'>och återigen på 1900-talet.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='sv'>Pusan glömmer aldrig sina hjältar, och i närheten av
Chungnyeolsa-templet
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='sv'>kan du besöka gravplatsen för de soldater
som dog när de försvarade sin hemstad
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='sv'>mot belägrande japanska trupper
1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='sv'>År 1950 hamnade Pusan under belägring ännu en gång.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='sv'>Vid FN:s minneskyrkogård
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='sv'>kan du besöka gravarna tillhörande ca 140 000 stupade soldater,
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='sv'>som konstruerade de sista skyttegravarna runt Pusan
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='sv'>och slog tillbaka vågor av nordkoreanska soldater.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='sv'>Pusan var en av de få sydkoreanska städer
som inte föll under Koreakriget,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='sv'>vilket gjorde staden till en tillflyktsort för mer än 500 000 krigsflyktingar.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='sv'>Vid UN Peace Memorial Hall
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='sv'>hedras uppoffringarna av både soldater
och civila,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='sv'>liksom berättelserna om lidandet från
pågående konflikter runt jorden.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='sv'>Pusan har mycket att tacka sina motståndskraftiga krigsflyktingar för.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='sv'>De maträtter som uppfanns under efterkrigsårens svårigheter har
fulländats till kulinariska mästerverk.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='sv'>En gränd där ett par brukade sälja tidningar som
amerikanska soldater kastat bort,
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='sv'>växte fram till att bli en gata fullspäckad med bokaffärer.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='sv'>Och ett fåtal anspråkslösa kiosker där nykomlingar
utbytte nödvändiga livsmedel,
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='sv'>är nu för tiden en av Koreas största och mest populära
traditionsenliga marknader.
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='sv'>Här säljs allt från kimchi till gymnastikskor.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='sv'>Pusans krigsflyktingar byggde först ut hamnsidans
områden med bostäder,
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='sv'>och därefter hundratals provisoriska hem
på de branta och karga höjderna runtom staden.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='sv'>Efter många år av hårt arbete
och flit
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='sv'>har Gamcheons lokalbefolkning blivit ett med sin
kreativa sida.
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='sv'>De dekorerar sina gator och husväggar med konstverk
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='sv'>som har förvandlat området
till en av stadens största sevärdheter.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='sv'>Gamcheons förvandling symboliserar Pusans
nyfunna, kreativa
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='sv'>och kulturella entreprenörsanda,
som har blommat upp över hela staden.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='sv'>Upplev denna energi på museer av världsklass,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='sv'>...gallerier,
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='sv'>...och festivaler.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='sv'>Hör ljudet av den på de livliga shoppinggatorna
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='sv'>och inuti en av världens största varuhus
på nästan 280 000 m2.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='sv'>Känn dofterna och smaka på maträtterna som lockar hit
matälskare och skaldjurskonnässörer från världens alla hörn.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='sv'>Och njut av atmosfären på kvällen när stadsljusen kastar sitt sken
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='sv'>över staden, precis som vid ljusshowen på den årliga
lyktfestivalen.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='sv'>Efter att ha hållit fienderna borta från sina
portar under århundraden och genomlidit årtionden av svårigheter
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='sv'>och slit, har denna sprudlande hamnstad äntligen
fått sin egen prägel.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='sv'>Idag är Pusan en bro som perfekt förbinder
det förflutna med framtiden.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='sv'>Välkommen till Pusan, en fest för alla sinnen
och för själen.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='sv'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='es-MX'>La ciudad de Busan está en la costa sureste
de la península de Corea,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='es-MX'>a solo un corto vuelo de capitales asiáticas,
como Beijing y Tokio,
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='es-MX'>y a un viaje de dos horas y media en tren bala
de Seúl.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='es-MX'>El mayor puerto y la segunda ciudad más grande de Corea del Sur
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='es-MX'>se extiende a lo largo de la escarpada costa
de la región de Yeongnam,
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='es-MX'>y se eleva en un mar de montañas a lo lejos.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='es-MX'>Desde los mariscos que atrajeron a recolectores
paleolíticos a sus litorales escabrosos,
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='es-MX'>hasta las interminables opciones del
mercado de pescado de Jagalchi,
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='es-MX'>desde los barcos antiguos de Joseon,
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='es-MX'>hasta los astilleros que ayudaron a impulsar
el milagro económico de Corea del Sur,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='es-MX'>Busan siempre ha estado ligada al mar.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='es-MX'>A medida que el mundo se adentra más en el siglo XXI,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='es-MX'>Busan sigue evolucionando
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='es-MX'>para convertirse en un paraíso donde los coreanos trabajadores
pueden relajarse,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='es-MX'>reflexionar sobre el pasado,
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='es-MX'>y mirar hacia el futuro.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='es-MX'>Mientras que el bullicioso puerto es la base de la
vitalidad económica de Busan,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='es-MX'>son las playas de la ciudad las que atraen
a cada vez más viajeros de toda Asia.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='es-MX'>A solo 40 minutos en metro de la estación de Busan
se encuentra la atracción principal de la ciudad,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='es-MX'>la playa Haeundae, el lugar junto a la playa
más grande y más amado de Corea del Sur.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='es-MX'>Sigue la gran extensión de arena hacia el este
hasta llegar a la colina Dalmaji,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='es-MX'>un mirador adorado por los poetas errantes
de antaño
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='es-MX'>y los amantes del café de ahora.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='es-MX'>Del extremo este de Haeundae,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='es-MX'>toma los senderos que atraviesan el parque Dongbaek hasta APEC House,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='es-MX'>donde los líderes de Asia y el Pacífico disfrutaron
de algunas de las mejores vistas de Busan
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='es-MX'>durante su cumbre en 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='es-MX'>La siempre cambiante costa de Busan ofrece paisajes
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='es-MX'>y actividades para todos los estados de ánimo.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='es-MX'>Para una relajación total,
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='es-MX'>acomoda tu toalla en la curva de media luna
de playa Gwangalli,
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='es-MX'>y disfruta el agua tranquila,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='es-MX'>el ambiente relajado
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='es-MX'>y las vistas del puente Gwangan.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='es-MX'>Si buscas una aventura,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='es-MX'>súbete a un barco en el pueblo pesquero de Cheongsapo.
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='es-MX'>O visita el mirador en el extremo
de la península de Yongho-Dong
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='es-MX'>y disfruta las vistas de las islas Oryukdo
cerca en la costa.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='es-MX'>¿Buscas iluminación?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='es-MX'>Dirígete a Gijang
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='es-MX'>y pide un deseo en el
templo Haedong Yonggungsa,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='es-MX'>uno de los pocos templos budistas en Corea construido
junto al mar.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='es-MX'>Cruza el histórico puente Yeongdodaegyo
y dirígete al parque Taejongdae.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='es-MX'>Fue en estos acantilados donde,
de acuerdo a la leyenda,
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='es-MX'>dioses y diosas vinieron una vez a relajarse
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='es-MX'>y el 29º rey de Silla pasó su tiempo libre
disparando flechas a las nubes que pasan.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='es-MX'>Para los simples mortales de hoy,
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='es-MX'>el parque es el lugar perfecto para
entrar en un estado de relajación
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='es-MX'>mientras los barcos de carga viajan hacia puertos lejanos.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='es-MX'>Este estado de ánimo meditativo también se encuentra en playa Songdo.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='es-MX'>Atraviesa las aguas turbulentas
por el puente elevado,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='es-MX'>cuyas curvas representan un dragón mítico
emprendiendo vuelo desde su guarida costera.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='es-MX'>Luego, deja que tu mente deambule y que los niños
corran libremente en la playa Dadaepo.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='es-MX'>Aquí, en la desembocadura del río más largo de Corea del Sur,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='es-MX'>las interminables arenas y nieblas marinas desdibujan las líneas
entre el cielo y la tierra.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='es-MX'>Aunque la historia de Busan ha sido continuamente
moldeada por el mar,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='es-MX'>a esta ciudad también la definen sus montañas.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='es-MX'>Justo arriba del puerto,
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='es-MX'>sube por las escaleras eléctricas hasta la cima del parque Yongdusan
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='es-MX'>y comparte las vistas con la estatua del
héroe naval del siglo XIX,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='es-MX'>el almirante Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='es-MX'>En el cercano monte Cheonma,
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='es-MX'>camina 20 minutos hasta llegar al mirador
para ver a la ciudad dinámica de Busan
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='es-MX'>frente a ti.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='es-MX'>En el norte de la ciudad,
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='es-MX'>sube a bordo de un teleférico durante cinco minutos
para llegar al parque Geumgang,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='es-MX'>donde se encuentra el pico más alto de Busan.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='es-MX'>Acompaña a los miles de residentes que caminan aquí
cada fin de semana
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='es-MX'>y exploran los muros y los senderos del bosque 
de la Fortaleza de Geumgang.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='es-MX'>También en el parque está el templo Beomeosa,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='es-MX'>cuyos monjes guerreros lucharon contra los invasores
en el siglo XVI
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='es-MX'>y otra vez en el siglo XX.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='es-MX'>Busan nunca olvida a sus héroes, y en el cercano
templo Chungnyeolsa,
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='es-MX'>rinde respeto a los espíritus de los
patriotas de Busan que perdieron la vida
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='es-MX'>cuando su ciudad fue sitiada por tropas japonesas
en 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='es-MX'>En 1950, Busan volvió a estar bajo asedio.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='es-MX'>En el cementerio conmemorativo de la ONU,
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='es-MX'>visita las tumbas de algunos de los 140,000 soldados
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='es-MX'>que formaron un perímetro de última línea de defensa alrededor de Busan
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='es-MX'>y lucharon contra oleadas de soldados norcoreanos.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='es-MX'>Busan fue una de las pocas ciudades del sur
que no fue derrotada en la Guerra de Corea,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='es-MX'>convirtiéndose en un refugio seguro para más de medio millón de refugiados.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='es-MX'>En la sala conmemorativa de la paz de la ONU,
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='es-MX'>los sacrificios tanto de combatientes como civiles
son recordados,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='es-MX'>así como las historias de sufrimiento por los continuos
conflictos en todo el mundo.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='es-MX'>Busan debe mucho a sus fuertes refugiados.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='es-MX'>Los platillos que surgieron de las dificultades de la posguerra han sido
perfeccionados en obras maestras culinarias.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='es-MX'>Un callejón donde una pareja de refugiados vendía revistas
que desechaban los soldados americanos
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='es-MX'>se convirtió en una calle entera de librerías.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='es-MX'>Y unos pocos puestos humildes donde los recién llegados
intercambiaban lo básico de la vida
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='es-MX'>es ahora uno de los más grandes y queridos
mercados tradicionales de Corea,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='es-MX'>que vende de todo, desde Kimchi hasta tenis.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='es-MX'>Los refugiados de Busan primero llenaron
la zona del puerto,
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='es-MX'>antes de construir cientos de casas improvisadas
en las empinadas y vacías colinas alrededor de la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='es-MX'>Después de años de trabajar
arduamente,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='es-MX'>los residentes de Gamcheon usaron su
creatividad
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='es-MX'>para adornar sus callejones y muros con obras de arte
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='es-MX'>y transformar esta área
en una de las principales atracciones turísticas de la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='es-MX'>El cambio de imagen de Gamcheon simboliza
la nueva energía creativa,
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='es-MX'>cultural y empresarial de Busan
que ha florecido por toda la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='es-MX'>Encontrarás esta energía en sus museos,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='es-MX'>galerías
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='es-MX'>y festivales.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='es-MX'>La escucharás en el alegre bullicio de sus calles comerciales
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='es-MX'>y en los 280,000 metros cuadrados de
la tienda departamental más grande del mundo.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='es-MX'>La olerás y probarás en una cocina que atrae
a amantes de la comida y de los mariscos de todo el mundo.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='es-MX'>Y la sentirás cuando la ciudad se ilumina todas las noches,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='es-MX'>así como con su festival anual
de linternas.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='es-MX'>Después de siglos de mantener a los enemigos alejados de sus
puertas, y décadas de dificultades y trabajo,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='es-MX'>esta alegre ciudad portuaria por fin ha llegado
a su apogeo.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='es-MX'>La actual ciudad de Busan es un puente que conecta perfectamente
el pasado y el futuro en un presente muy especial.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='es-MX'>Bienvenido a Busan, una fiesta para todos los sentidos
y para el alma.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='es-MX'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='es-ES'>La ciudad de Busan se encuentra en la costa sureste
de la península de Corea,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='es-ES'>a poca distancia en avión de capitales asiáticas
como Pekín y Tokio,
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='es-ES'>y a solo dos horas y media en tren bala
de Seúl.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='es-ES'>El principal puerto y segunda ciudad de Corea del Sur
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='es-ES'>se extiende a lo largo de la escarpada costa
de la región de Yeongnam
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='es-ES'>y se eleva sobre un mar de montañas.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='es-ES'>Desde el marisco que atrajo a los recolectores
paleolíticos a sus abruptas costas
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='es-ES'>hasta la casi interminable oferta
de la lonja de pescado de Jagalchi,
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='es-ES'>así como desde la antigua flota de la dinastía Joseon
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='es-ES'>hasta los astilleros que impulsaron
el milagro económico nacional,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='es-ES'>Busan siempre ha estado muy vinculada al mar.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='es-ES'>Mientras el mundo se adentra en el siglo XXI,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='es-ES'>Busan no deja de evolucionar
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='es-ES'>hacia un enclave en el que sus residentes
pueden relajarse,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='es-ES'>reflexionar sobre el pasado
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='es-ES'>y escudriñar el futuro.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='es-ES'>Aunque su concurrido puerto sustenta
la vitalidad económica de la ciudad,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='es-ES'>son sus playas las que, cada vez más,
atraen a viajeros de toda Asia.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='es-ES'>A solo 40 minutos en metro de la estación de Busan
se encuentra su atracción estrella,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='es-ES'>la playa de Haeundae, la zona costera más grande
y apreciada de Corea del Sur.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='es-ES'>Recorre el extenso tramo de arena hacia al este
hasta la colina de Dalmaji,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='es-ES'>un mirador muy apreciado por los poetas errantes
de antaño
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='es-ES'>y los amantes del café de hoy en día.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='es-ES'>No te vayas del extremo este de Haeundae
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='es-ES'>sin atravesar el parque de Dongbaek hasta la casa APEC,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='es-ES'>donde los líderes asiáticos y del Pacífico disfrutaron
de las mejores vistas de Busan
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='es-ES'>durante la cumbre de 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='es-ES'>La siempre cambiante costa de Busan
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='es-ES'>cuenta con paisajes y actividades para todos los gustos.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='es-ES'>Si buscas relajarte,
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='es-ES'>extiende tu toalla sobre la media luna
de la playa de Gwangalli
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='es-ES'>y disfruta de sus serenas aguas,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='es-ES'>su ambiente tranquilo
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='es-ES'>y sus vistas del puente de Diamante.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='es-ES'>Si, por el contrario, buscas aventura,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='es-ES'>súbete a un barco en la aldea pesquera de Cheongsapo
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='es-ES'>o recorre el paso elevado en el extremo
de la península de Yongho-Dong
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='es-ES'>y admira las vistas de las islas de Oryukdo
mar adentro.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='es-ES'>¿Buscas un poco de iluminación?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='es-ES'>Entonces ve a Gijang
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='es-ES'>y pide un deseo en el templo de Haedong
Yonggungsa,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='es-ES'>uno de los pocos templos budistas de Corea
construidos junto al mar.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='es-ES'>Cruza el histórico puente de Yeongdodaegyo
hacia el parque de Taejongdae.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='es-ES'>Fue en estos acantilados donde,
según la leyenda,
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='es-ES'>los dioses bajaron a relajarse,
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='es-ES'>y donde el 29.º rey de Silla disfrutaba
disparando flechas a las nubes que pasaban.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='es-ES'>Actualmente,
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='es-ES'>el parque es el lugar perfecto
para tomarse la vida con calma
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='es-ES'>mientras los cargueros parten hacia puertos lejanos.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='es-ES'>Continúa con la meditación en la playa de Songdo.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='es-ES'>Cruza las aguas revueltas sobre la pasarela
elevada,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='es-ES'>cuyas curvas forman un dragón mítico
que levantan el vuelo de su refugio costero.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='es-ES'>Después, deja vagar la mente y a los niños correr
a sus anchas en la playa de Dadaepo.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='es-ES'>En la boca del río más largo de Corea del Sur,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='es-ES'>las arenas infinitas y la bruma marina difuminan la línea
entre el cielo y la tierra.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='es-ES'>Aunque la historia de Busan siempre ha estado
influenciada por el mar,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='es-ES'>las montañas también son importantes en la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='es-ES'>Justo sobre el puerto,
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='es-ES'>sube las escaleras hasta la cima del parque de Yongdusan
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='es-ES'>y comparte las vistas con la estatua
del almirante Yi Sun Sin,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='es-ES'>héroe naval del siglo XVI.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='es-ES'>En el cercano monte de Cheonma,
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='es-ES'>haz un recorrido de 20 minutos hasta el puesto
de observación para ver &quot;Dynamic Busan&quot;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='es-ES'>a tus pies.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='es-ES'>Al norte de la ciudad,
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='es-ES'>móntate en el teleférico para disfrutar de un trayecto
de cinco minutos hasta el parque de Geumgang,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='es-ES'>hogar del pico más alto de Busan.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='es-ES'>Únete a miles de residentes que pasean
por la zona los fines de semana
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='es-ES'>y explora los senderos y los muros 
de la fortaleza de Geumjeong.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='es-ES'>El parque también alberga el templo de Beomeosa,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='es-ES'>cuyos monjes lucharon contra los invasores
durante el siglo XVI
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='es-ES'>y de nuevo en el XX.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='es-ES'>Busan no olvida a sus héroes, y en el cercano
templo de Chungnyeolsa
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='es-ES'>podrás presentar tus respetos a las almas
de los patriotas que dieron su vida
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='es-ES'>cuando la ciudad fue cercada por las tropas japonesas
en 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='es-ES'>En 1950, Busan volvió a ser asediada.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='es-ES'>En el cementerio conmemorativo de la ONU
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='es-ES'>podrás visitar las tumbas de algunos de los 140 000 soldados
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='es-ES'>que formaron un desesperado perímetro en torno a Busan
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='es-ES'>y se enfrentaron a las tropas norcoreanas.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='es-ES'>Busan fue una de las pocas ciudades del sur
que no cayeron durante la guerra de Corea,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='es-ES'>y acogió a más de medio millón de refugiados.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='es-ES'>En el Centro Conmemorativo de la Paz de la ONU
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='es-ES'>se recuerda el sacrificio de los combatientes
y los civiles,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='es-ES'>además de los relatos de sufrimiento de los conflictos
inacabados de todo el mundo.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='es-ES'>Busan está en deuda con sus tenaces refugiados.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='es-ES'>Los platos surgidos de las penurias de la posguerra
se han perfeccionado hasta ser joyas culinarias.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='es-ES'>La callejuela donde una pareja vendía revistas
dejadas por los soldados americanos
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='es-ES'>se ha convertido en una calle de librerías.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='es-ES'>Y los humildes puestos donde los recién llegados
intercambiaban productos básicos
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='es-ES'>es ahora uno de los mercados tradicionales
más grandes y apreciados de Corea,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='es-ES'>donde se vende desde kimchi hasta zapatillas.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='es-ES'>Los refugiados de Busan vivieron
en las zonas del puerto
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='es-ES'>antes de construir cientos de casas improvisadas
en las empinadas colinas que rodean la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='es-ES'>Tras años de trabajo dejándose
la piel,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='es-ES'>los residentes de Gamcheon
han dado rienda suelta a su creatividad
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='es-ES'>y adornan las calles y paredes con obras de arte
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='es-ES'>que han transformado el barrio
en una de las principales atracciones de la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='es-ES'>La renovación de Gamcheon simboliza la reciente
ola creativa,
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='es-ES'>cultural y emprendedora de Busan,
que ha florecido por toda la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='es-ES'>Podrás ver esta energía en los geniales museos,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='es-ES'>galerías
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='es-ES'>y festivales de la ciudad.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='es-ES'>Oírla en el alegre trajín de las calles comerciales
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='es-ES'>y en los casi trescientos mil metros cuadrados
del mayor centro comercial del mundo.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='es-ES'>Olerla y probarla en una cocina que seduce
a gourmets y amantes del marisco de todas partes.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='es-ES'>Y sentirla al llenarse la ciudad de luz por las noches,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='es-ES'>como en las exhibiciones del festival anual
de faroles.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='es-ES'>Tras siglos manteniendo alejados a los enemigos
de sus puertas y décadas de dificultades y pesar,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='es-ES'>esta alegre ciudad portuaria por fin se muestra
como es.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='es-ES'>Hoy Busan es un puente que conecta a la perfección
el pasado y el futuro en un presente de lo más especial.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='es-ES'>Te damos la bienvenida a Busan, un festival
para los sentidos y el alma.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='es-ES'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='en'>The city of Busan sits on the Korean Peninsula’s
south-eastern coastline,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='en'>just a short flight from Asian capitals like
Beijing and Tokyo,
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='en'>and a two-and-a-half hour bullet train ride
from Seoul.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='en'>South Korea’s largest port and second-largest city
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='en'>spreads out along the jagged coastline of
the Yeongnam Region,
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='en'>and rises into a sea of mountains beyond.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='en'>From the shellfish which drew Paleolithic
gatherers to its rugged shores,
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='en'>to the never-ending offerings of Jagalchi
Fish Market,
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='en'>…from the Joseon ships of old,
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='en'>to the dockyards which helped drive South
Korea’s economic miracle,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='en'>Busan has forever been linked to the ocean.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='en'>As the world races further into the 21st century,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='en'>Busan continues to evolve,
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='en'>into a haven where hard-working Koreans can
let their hair down,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='en'>reflect on the past,
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='en'>and peer into the future.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='en'>While the bustling port underpins Busan’s
economic vitality,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='en'>it’s the city’s beaches which increasingly
draw travellers from all over Asia.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='en'>Just a 40-minute subway ride from Busan Station
is the city’s star attraction,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='en'>Haeundae Beach, South Korea’s biggest and
best-loved beachside hangout.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='en'>Follow the long sweep of sands eastward to
Dalmaji Hill,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='en'>an outlook adored by the wandering poets of
yesteryear
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='en'>and the coffee lovers of today.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='en'>While at Haeundae’s eastern end,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='en'>take the paths through Dongbaek Park to APEC House,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='en'>where Asian and Pacific leaders enjoyed some
of Busan’s most celebrated views
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='en'>during their 2005 summit.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='en'>Busan’s ever-changing coastline offers scenery
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='en'>and activities to match your every mood.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='en'>For total relaxation,
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='en'>unroll your towel on the half-moon curve of
Gwangalli Beach,
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='en'>and enjoy gentle waters,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='en'>laid-back vibes,
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='en'>and views to Diamond Bridge.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='en'>If you’re looking for adventure,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='en'>join a charter at the fishing village of Cheongsapo.
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='en'>Or step out onto the skywalk at the end of
the Yongho-Dong Peninsula,
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='en'>and take in the views of the Oryukdo Islands
just offshore.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='en'>Seeking a little enlightenment?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='en'>Head to Gijang,
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='en'>and make a wish at the Haedong Yonggungsa
Temple,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='en'>one of the few Buddhist temples in Korea built
by the ocean.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='en'>Cross historic Yeongdodaegyo Bridge and head
to Taejongdae Park.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='en'>It was at these cliffs where, according to
legend,
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='en'>gods and goddesses once came to relax,
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='en'>and the 29th King of Silla spent his leisure
time shooting arrows into the passing clouds.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='en'>For today’s mere mortals,
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='en'>the park&#39;s the perfect place to slip into
a slower state of mind
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='en'>as cargo ships journey to far off ports.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='en'>The meditative mood continues at Songdo Beach.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='en'>Step across the swirling waters on the elevated
walkway,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='en'>whose curves depict a mythical dragon taking
flight from it’s coastal lair.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='en'>Then, let your mind wander and the kids run
free at Dadaepo Beach.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='en'>Here, at the mouth of South Korea’s longest river,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='en'>the endless sands and sea mists blur the lines
between heaven and earth.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='en'>While Busan’s story has been continually
shaped by the sea,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='en'>it’s a city equally defined by its mountains.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='en'>Just above the port,
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='en'>ride the escalator to the summit of Yongdusan Park
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='en'>and share the views with the statue of 16th
century naval hero,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='en'>Admiral Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='en'>On nearby Mt Cheonma,
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='en'>take the 20-minute hike to the observation
platform to see “Dynamic Busan”
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='en'>spread out before you.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='en'>In the city’s north,
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='en'>climb aboard a cable car for the five-minute
ride to Geumgang Park,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='en'>the home to Busan’s highest peak.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='en'>Join the thousands of locals who hike here
each weekend,
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='en'>exploring the forest trails and walls 
of Geumgang Fortress.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='en'>The park is also home to Beomeosa Temple,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='en'>whose warrior monks fought off invaders in
the 16th century,
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='en'>and again in the 20th.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='en'>Busan never forgets its heroes, and at nearby
Chungnyeolsa Temple,
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='en'>pay your respects to the spirits of Busan’s
patriots who gave their lives
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='en'>when their city was besieged by Japanese troops
in 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='en'>In 1950, Busan was again under siege.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='en'>At the UN Memorial Cemetery,
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='en'>visit the gravesites of some of the 140,000 troops
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='en'>who formed a last-ditch perimeter around Busan,
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='en'>fighting off waves of North Korean soldiers.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='en'>Busan was one of the few cities of the south
not to fall during the Korean War,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='en'>becoming a safe haven for over half a million refugees.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='en'>At the UN Peace Memorial Hall,
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='en'>the sacrifices of both combatants and civilians
are remembered,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='en'>as are the stories of suffering from ongoing
conflicts around the globe.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='en'>Busan owes much to it’s resilient refugees.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='en'>Dishes born of post-war hardship have been
perfected into culinary masterpieces.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='en'>An alleyway where a refugee couple sold magazines
discarded by American GIs
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='en'>grew into an entire street of bookshops.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='en'>And a few humble stalls where the newcomers
traded life’s basics
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='en'>is now one of Korea’s biggest and best-loved
traditional markets,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='en'>selling everything from Kimchi to sneakers.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='en'>Busan’s refugees first filled the portside
areas,
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='en'>before building hundreds of makeshift homes
on the steep barren hills around the city.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='en'>After years of keeping their noses to the
grindstone,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='en'>the residents of Gamcheon have embraced their
creative side,
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='en'>adorning their laneways and walls with artworks
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='en'>which have transformed their neighbourhood
into one of the city’s top tourist attractions.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='en'>Gamcheon’s makeover symbolises Busan’s
new-found creative,
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='en'>cultural and entrepreneurial energy which
has blossomed all over the city.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='en'>See this energy in its world-class museums,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='en'>…galleries,
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='en'>…and festivals.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='en'>Hear it, in the happy bustle of its shopping streets,
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='en'>and across the three-million-square-feet of
the world’s largest department store.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='en'>Smell it; Taste it, in a cuisine which lures
foodies and seafood lovers from all over the globe.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='en'>And feel it, as the city erupts in light each night,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='en'>just like the displays of its annual lantern
festival.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='en'>After centuries of keeping enemies from its
gates, and decades of hardship and toil,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='en'>this rollicking port town has at last come
into its own.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='en'>Today’s Busan is a bridge, perfectly connecting
the past and future into a very special now.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='en'>Welcome to Busan, a feast for all the senses,
and the soul.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='en'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='it'>La città di Busan si trova
sulla costa sud-orientale della penisola coreana,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='it'>a poche ore di volo
da altre capitali asiatiche come Pechino o Tokyo
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='it'>e a solo due ore e mezza da Seoul
con un treno ad alta velocità.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='it'>È la città portuale più grande e la seconda in generale della Corea del Sud
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='it'>e si estende lungo la costa frastagliata
della regione di Yeongnam,
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='it'>con una catena montuosa che le fa da sfondo.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='it'>Dai molluschi che hanno attirato
gli uomini del Paleolitico sulle sue coste irregolari
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='it'>fino all’offerta infinita
del mercato del pesce di Jagalchi...
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='it'>...o dalle vecchie navi della dinastia Joseon
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='it'>fino ai cantieri navali che hanno sostenuto
il miracolo economico della Corea del Sud,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='it'>Busan da sempre è associata al mare.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='it'>Mentre il mondo continua la sua corsa nel 21° secolo,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='it'>Busan non smette di trasformarsi
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='it'>in un&#39;isola felice
dove gli infaticabili lavoratori coreani possono riposarsi,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='it'>riflettere sul passato
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='it'>e dare una sbirciata al futuro.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='it'>Anche se è il trafficato porto di Busan
a sostenere la sua economia,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='it'>sono le spiagge della città
ad attirare sempre più turisti provenienti da tutta l’Asia.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='it'>A solo 40 minuti di autobus
dalla stazione di Busan si trova la sua attrazione principale,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='it'>la spiaggia di Haeundae, la più grande della Corea
e uno dei punti di ritrovo balneari più amati.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='it'>Dirigendovi verso est,
seguite la lunga striscia di sabbia fino alla collina Dalmaji,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='it'>un punto panoramico
molto amato dai poeti itineranti di ieri
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='it'>e dagli amanti del caffè di oggi.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='it'>Mentre siete all&#39;estremità orientale di Haeundae,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='it'>incamminatevi sul percorso che va dal parco Dongbaek alla APEC House,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='it'>dove i leader asiatici e del Pacifico
hanno ammirato alcuni dei panorami più celebri di Busan,
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='it'>durante il summit del 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='it'>La costa di Busan, in continuo mutamento,
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='it'>offre panorami e attività che soddisferanno ogni capriccio.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='it'>Per immergervi nel relax più totale,
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='it'>srotolate il telo da mare
lungo la curva a mezzaluna della spiaggia Gwangalli
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='it'>e godetevi le sue acque calme,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='it'>la sua atmosfera rilassata
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='it'>e la vista sul ponte Diamond.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='it'>Se siete in cerca di avventura,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='it'>non perdetevi il villaggio di pescatori di Cheongsapo,
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='it'>oppure passeggiate sulla passerella sopraelevata
all’estremità della penisola di Yongho-Dong
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='it'>per ammirare al meglio
il panorama delle vicine isole Oryukdo.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='it'>Cercate un po&#39; di ispirazione mistica?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='it'>Andate a Gijang
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='it'>ed esprimete un desiderio
nel tempio di Haedong Yonggungsa,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='it'>uno dei rari templi buddisti coreani
a pochi passi dal mare.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='it'>Attraversate lo storico ponte Yeongdodaegyo
e incamminatevi verso il parco Taejongdae.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='it'>Secondo la leggenda,
su queste scogliere
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='it'>le divinità venivano a rilassarsi
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='it'>e il 29° re del regno di Silla
passava il tempo libero scoccando frecce alle nubi di passaggio.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='it'>Per i semplici mortali di oggi,
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='it'>il parco è il posto perfetto
per dimenticare ogni pensiero
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='it'>osservando le navi mercantili dirette in porti lontani.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='it'>L’atmosfera meditativa prosegue sulla spiaggia di Songdo.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='it'>Superate le sue acque vorticose
grazie alla passerella sopraelevata,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='it'>le cui curve raffigurano
un drago mitologico che spicca il volo dalla sua tana costiera.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='it'>Lasciate quindi vagare la mente
mentre i più piccoli corrono felici sulla spiaggia Dadaepo.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='it'>Qui, alla foce del fiume più lungo della Corea del Sud,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='it'>la sabbia infinita e la foschia marina
confondono il tenue confine fra la terra e il paradiso.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='it'>Anche se la storia di Busan
è stata sempre plasmata dal mare,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='it'>le montagne sono altrettanto importanti per la città.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='it'>Proprio sopra al porto,
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='it'>prendete la scala mobile verso la cima del parco Yongdusan
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='it'>e ammirate il panorama
in compagnia della statua dell’eroe navale del 16° secolo,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='it'>l’Ammiraglio Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='it'>Dal vicino monte Cheonma
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='it'>seguite per circa 20 minuti il percorso che vi porterà
a una piattaforma dove potrete osservare la “Dynamic Busan”
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='it'>che si estende davanti ai vostri occhi.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='it'>Nella parte nord della città
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='it'>salite su una funivia che vi condurrà,
in circa cinque minuti, al parco Geumgang,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='it'>dove si trova la cima più alta di Busan.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='it'>Unitevi alle migliaia di persone della zona che ogni fine settimana
la scelgono come meta per le escursioni,
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='it'>esplorando i sentieri immersi nel verde 
e le mura della fortezza di Geumgang.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='it'>Qui c&#39;è anche il tempio di Beomeosa,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='it'>casa dei monaci guerrieri
che hanno combattuto e respinto gli invasori nel 16° secolo
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='it'>e poi di nuovo nel 20°.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='it'>Busan non dimentica i suoi eroi
e nel vicino tempio di Chungnyeolsa
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='it'>potrete porgere i vostri omaggi
agli spiriti dei patrioti di Busan che sacrificarono la loro vita
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='it'>quando la città venne assediata
dalle truppe giapponesi nel 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='it'>Nel 1950, Busan finì di nuovo sotto assedio.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='it'>Nel Cimitero memoriale delle Nazioni Unite
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='it'>potrete osservare le tombe di alcuni dei 140.000 soldati
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='it'>che formarono un perimetro difensivo d’emergenza attorno a Busan,
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='it'>cercando di respingere le armate nordcoreane.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='it'>Busan è stata una delle poche città
della Corea del Sud a non cadere durante la guerra di Corea,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='it'>diventando un porto franco per oltre mezzo milione di rifugiati.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='it'>Nel Memoriale della pace delle Nazioni Unite
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='it'>viene ricordato il sacrificio,
sia dei soldati che dei civili,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='it'>così come le storie delle sofferenze
causate dai conflitti in tutto il mondo.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='it'>Busan deve molto alla perseveranza dei suoi rifugiati.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='it'>Piatti che sono nati nelle difficoltà del dopoguerra
si sono trasformati in capolavori culinari.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='it'>Un vicolo in cui una coppia di rifugiati
vendeva i giornali scartati dai soldati americani
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='it'>si è trasformato in un’intera via piena di librerie.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='it'>Alcune delle semplici bancarelle
dove i nuovi arrivati vendevano beni di prima necessità
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='it'>sono cresciute fino a diventare
uno dei mercati coreani tradizionali più grandi e popolari
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='it'>dove troverete di tutto, dal kimchi alle sneaker.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='it'>I rifugiati di Busan
agli inizi popolarono la zona del porto,
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='it'>ma poi costruirono centinaia di case di fortuna
ai piedi delle colline che circondano la città.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='it'>Dopo tanti anni
di duro lavoro,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='it'>gli abitanti di Gamcheon
hanno dato sfogo al loro lato creativo,
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='it'>decorando le strade e i muri del quartiere con opere d’arte
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='it'>e trasformando così la zona
in una delle più belle attrazioni cittadine.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='it'>Il nuovo stile di Gamcheon
è un simbolo della nuova energia creativa,
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='it'>culturale e imprenditoriale
che è esplosa in tutta la città.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='it'>Potrete percepirla nei suoi musei di fama mondiale...
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='it'>...nelle sue gallerie d’arte...
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='it'>...e nei suoi festival.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='it'>Ascoltatela nell&#39;allegro viavai delle vie dello shopping
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='it'>e negli oltre 270.000 metri quadrati
del centro commerciale più grande del mondo.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='it'>Sentitene il profumo e il sapore
in una cucina amata dai buongustai di tutto il mondo.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='it'>Osservatela ogni notte quando la città brilla di luci,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='it'>come accade
durante l’annuale festival delle lanterne.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='it'>Dopo secoli passati a tener lontani i nemici
e dopo decenni di fatiche e avversità,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='it'>questa allegra città portuale
ha infine trovato la sua dimensione.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='it'>Busan oggi è un ponte,
che collega passato e futuro in un presente molto speciale.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='it'>Benvenuti a Busan,
un vera festa per i sensi e per lo spirito.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='it'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='id'>Kota Busan berada di garis pantai
Tenggara Semenanjung Korea,
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='id'>penerbangan singkat dari ibu kota Asia seperti
Beijing dan Tokyo,
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='id'>dan dua jam setengah naik kereta peluru
dari Seoul.
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='id'>Pelabuhan terbesar dan kota kedua terbesar di Korea Selatan
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='id'>membentang sepanjang garis pantai
Wilayah Yeongnam,
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='id'>dan menjulang di antara perbukitan tepi pantai.
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='id'>Dari kerang yang menarik pengumpul Paleolitik
ke pantai kasarnya,
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='id'>hingga ke Pasar Ikan Jagalchi
yang memiliki penawaran tak terbatas,
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='id'>…dari kapal kuno Joseon,
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='id'>hingga galangan kapal yang membantu mendorong
keajaiban ekonomi Korea Selatan,
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='id'>Busan selamanya dikaitkan dengan laut.
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='id'>Ketika dunia berkembang semakin jauh memasuki abad ke-21,
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='id'>Busan terus berkembang,
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='id'>menjadi tempat singgah di mana orang Korea pekerja keras dapat
bersantai,
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='id'>merenungkan masa lalu,
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='id'>dan berlayar ke masa depan.
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='id'>Meskipun pelabuhan sibuk yang menyokong
kekuatan ekonomi Busan,
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='id'>namun pantai kota inilah yang memikat
semakin banyak traveler dari seluruh Asia.
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='id'>Hanya 40 menit naik kereta bawah tanah dari Stasiun Busan
terdapat objek wisata terpopuler kota ini,
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='id'>Pantai Haeundae, tepi patai tempat bergaul
terbesar dan terfavorit di Korea Selatan.
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='id'>Ikuti bentangan panjang pasing pantai ke arah timur
ke Bukit Dalmaji,
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='id'>pemadangan yang dipuja oleh penyair yang mengembara
di masa lalu
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='id'>dan pecinta kopi masa kini.
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='id'>Sementara di ujung timur Haeundae,
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='id'>ikuti jalan setapak melewati Taman Dongbaek ke Gedung APEC,
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='id'>di mana pemimpin negara Asia dan Pasifik menikmati
pemandangan Busan yang paling memesona
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='id'>selama pertemuan mereka pada tahun 2005.
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='id'>Pantai Busan yang selalu berubah-ubah menawarkan pemandangan
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='id'>dan aktivitas yang sesuai dengan suasana hati Anda.
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='id'>Untuk relaksasi total,
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='id'>berjemurlah di pantai yang melengkung berbentuk bulan setengah
Pantai Gwangalli,
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='id'>dan nikmati air yang lemut,
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='id'>suasana santai,
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='id'>dan pemandangan ke arah Diamond Bridge.
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='id'>Jika Anda mencari petualangan,
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='id'>bergabunglah dengan kapal sewaan di desa nelayan Cheongsapo.
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='id'>Atau berjalan di skywalk di ujung
Semenanjung Yongho-Dong,
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='id'>dan nikmati pemandangan Kepulauan Oryukdo
di lepas pantai.
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='id'>Mencari pencerahan?
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='id'>Pergilah ke Gijang,
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='id'>dan berdoa di Kuil
Haedong Yonggungsa,
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='id'>salah satu dari sedikit kuil Buddha di Korea
yang di bangun di tepi laut.
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='id'>Seberangi Jembatan Yeongdodaegyo yang bersejarah dan
pergilah ke Taman Taejongdae.
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='id'>yang berada di tebing ini di mana, menurut
legenda,
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='id'>dewa dan dewi pernah datang untuk bersantai di sini,
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='id'>dan Raja Silla ke-29 menghabiskan waktu luangnya
melepaskan anak panah ke awan yang lewat.
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='id'>Untuk manusia masa kini,
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='id'>taman ini merupakan tempat yang tepat untuk masuk
ke keadaan pikiran yang lebih tenang
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='id'>perjalanan kapal kargo ke pelabuhan yang jauh.
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='id'>Suasana meditatif berlanjut di Pantai Songdo.
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='id'>Berjalan di atas air yang berombak di
jalan setapak yang tinggi,
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='id'>yang berkelok menggambarkan mitos naga
yang terbang dari sarangnya di pesisir pantai.
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='id'>Lalu, biarkan pikiran Anda berkelana dan anak-anak berlarian
bebas di Pantai Dadaepo.
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='id'>Di sini, di muara sungai terpanjang di Korea Selatan,
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='id'>pasir tak berujung dan kabut pantai mengaburkan garis
antara surga dan dunia.
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='id'>Meski kisah tentang Busan terus
dibentuk oleh laut,
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='id'>Busan adalah kota yang juga dibentuk oleh pegunungannya.
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='id'>Di atas pelabuhan,
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='id'>naik eskalator ke puncak Taman Yongdusan
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='id'>dan nikmati pemandangan dengan patung dari
pahlawan angkatan laut abad ke-16,
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='id'>Laksamana Yi Sun Sin.
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='id'>Di dekat Gunung Cheonma,
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='id'>mendakilah 20 menit ke platform
observasi untuk melihat “Busan yang Dinamis”
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='id'>membentang di hadapan Anda.
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='id'>Di bagian utara kota,
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='id'>naik kereta gantung selama lima menit
ke Taman Geumgang,
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='id'>rumah bagi puncak tertinggi di Busan.
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='id'>Bergabunglah dengan ribuan warga lokal yang mendaki di sini
setiap akhir pekan,
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='id'>menjelajahi jalan setapak hutan dan tembok 
Benteng Geumgang.
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='id'>Taman ini juga merupakan rumah bagi Kuil Beomeosa,
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='id'>yang biksu prajuritnya berjuang melawan penjajah di
abad ke-16,
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='id'>dan lagi di abad ke-20.
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='id'>Busan tidak pernah melupakan pahlawannya, dan di dekatnya terdapat
Kuil Chungnyeolsa,
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='id'>berkunjunglah untuk memberi penghormatan kepada
jiwa-jiwa pahlawan Busan yang mengorbankan hidupnya
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='id'>ketika kota mereka dikepung oleh pasukan Jepang
pada tahun 1592.
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='id'>Pada tahun 1950, Busan kembali dikepung.
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='id'>Di Makam Peringatan PBB,
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='id'>kunjungi sebagian makam dari 140.000 pasukan
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='id'>yang membentuk parit perimeter terakhir di sekitar Busan,
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='id'>melawan serbuan prajurit Korea Selatan.
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='id'>Busan adalah salah satu kota di selatan
yang tidak jatuh selama Perang Korea,
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='id'>menjadi tempat yang aman bagi lebih dari setengah juta pengungsi.
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='id'>Di Aula Peringatan Perdamaian PBB,
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='id'>pengorbanan dari pejuang dan warga sipil
dikenang,
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='id'>dan juga kisah-kisah penderitaan dari
konflik yang sedang berlangsung di seluruh dunia.
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='id'>Busan berhutang banyak kepada para pengungsi yang tangguh.
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='id'>Makanan yang terlahir pascaperang telah
disempurnakan menjadi mahakarya kuliner.
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='id'>Gang di mana pasangan pengungsi menjual majalah
dibuang oleh GI Amerika
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='id'>berkembang menjadi toko buku di sepanjang jalan.
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='id'>Dan beberapa toko sederhana di mana para pendatang baru
menjual kebutuhan dasar hidup
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='id'>kini menjadi salah satu pasar tradisional
terbesar dan terfavorit di Korea,
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='id'>menjual semua dari Kimchi hingga sepatu.
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='id'>Pengungsi Busan adalah warga pertama yang tinggal di
area tepi pelabuhan,
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='id'>sebelum membangun ratusan rumah darurat
di bukit-bukit yang curam di sekitar kota.
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='id'>Setelah bertahun-tahun bekerja dengan
gerinda,
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='id'>penduduk Gamcheon telah menunjukkan
sisi kreatif mereka,
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='id'>menghiasi jalanan dan tembok mereka dengan karya seni
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='id'>yang telah mengubah lingkungan mereka
menjadi salah satu objek wisata kota yang populer.
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='id'>Perubahan Gamcheon menjadi simbol
energi kreatif,
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='id'>budaya, dan wisausaha Busan yang
telah berkembang pesat di seluruh kota.
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='id'>Saksikan energi ini di museum,
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='id'>…galeri,
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='id'>…dan festival kelas dunia.
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='id'>Dengarkan, di tengah kesibukan jalanan pusat perbelanjaan,
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='id'>dan di mal terbesar di dunia
dengan luas tiga juta kaki persegi.
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='id'>Cium; Cicipi makanan yang menarik
pecinta makanan dan pecinta hidangan laut dari seluruh dunia.
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='id'>Dan rasakan, saat kota bermandikan cahaya setiap malamnya,
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='id'>seperti apa yang ditampilkan di festival
lampion tahunan.
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='id'>Setelah berabad-abad menjauhkan musuhnya dari
Gerbang kotanya, dan berpuluh tahun dari kesulitan dan kerja keras,
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='id'>kota pelabuhan yang ramai ini
akhirnya menjadi mandiri.
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='id'>Kini Busan adalah jembatan, yang menghubungkan dengan sempurna
masa lalu dan masa depan menjadi masa kini yang spesial.
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='id'>Selamat datang di Busan, pesta untuk semua indera,
dan jiwa.
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='id'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='ja'>プサンは朝鮮半島の南東部にある
美しい海沿いの都市
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='ja'>東京や北京など
アジア主要都市からのアクセスも良好です
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='ja'>ソウルから高速列車を利用すれば
わずか 2 時間半
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='ja'>韓国屈指の貿易港 そして首都に次ぐ第二の都市
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='ja'>国内有数のリアス式海岸を誇る
ヨンナム地域
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='ja'>山々が連なる景色がどこまでも続き
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='ja'>旧石器時代の人々も好んで食した
海産物がこの入り江に集まります
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='ja'>チャガルチ市場は尽きることがない
自然の恵みあふれる魚市場
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='ja'>一方で プサンは朝鮮時代から
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='ja'>造船拠点として
韓国経済をけん引しました
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='ja'>まさに海なくしてプサンの発展はなかったのです
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='ja'>世界が熾烈な競争社会へと変わるなか
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='ja'>プサンはさらに発展を続けます
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='ja'>癒やしを求める人々が
ゆっくりと深呼吸し
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='ja'>時に過去に思いをはせ
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='ja'>そして未来の気配を感じる街
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='ja'>海運がプサンの
発展のカギであることには変わりなくても
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='ja'>この地のビーチに魅力を感じて訪れる
旅行者を受け入れてくれる懐の大きさも特徴です
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='ja'>プサン駅から地下鉄を利用して 40 分で
人気スポットが目の前に
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='ja'>海雲台は
愛してやまない憩いの場
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='ja'>海岸沿いを東に進めば
そこはタルマジ ヒル
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='ja'>かつて放浪詩人が
その美しさをたたえた場所
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='ja'>今ではコーヒーの名所
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='ja'>海雲台の東端に
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='ja'>冬柏公園を抜けると APEC ハウスが見えてきます
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='ja'>2005 年 APEC 首脳が
プサンの絶景を
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='ja'>ここで楽しみました
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='ja'>折々の変化を見せるプサンの海で
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='ja'>景色やレジャーを堪能
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='ja'>ただゆっくりと
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='ja'>タオルを砂浜に広げ
広安里ビーチの
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='ja'>穏やかな海で
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='ja'>安らぎの空間と
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='ja'>ダイアモンド ブリッジの眺めを満喫
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='ja'>冒険心を満たそうと思っているなら
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='ja'>青沙浦村のチャーター クルーズがおすすめです
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='ja'>龍湖洞半島の最先端で
スカイ ウォークから
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='ja'>目の前に広がる五六島の景色を
海の上から眺めます
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='ja'>仏の教えに触れるなら
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='ja'>機張へ足を延ばしてみましょう
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='ja'>海東龍宮寺で
願い事をしてみましょう
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='ja'>ここは 海のすぐそばに建立された
仏教寺院
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='ja'>歴史ある影島大橋を渡り
太宗台公園へ
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='ja'>伝説によれば
神と女神がこの崖で
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='ja'>つかの間の休息を楽しみ
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='ja'>新羅の第 29 代の王が休暇を過ごし
過ぎゆく雲に矢を放った景勝地
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='ja'>日常の雑踏を離れ
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='ja'>この公園に時を忘れて
ゆったりとした心で過ごします
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='ja'>海の彼方に向かう船のように
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='ja'>松島ビーチにも 清らかな空気が満ちています
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='ja'>渦潮を海上ウォークウェイから
眺めます
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='ja'>これは伝説の龍が海辺から
飛び立つ姿を表しています
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='ja'>多大浦ビーチは大人の休憩所
子どもの壮大な遊び場
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='ja'>韓国で最も長い川の河口であり
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='ja'>どこまでも続く砂浜と海霧
ここは天国でしょうか
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='ja'>プサンの歴史はずっと
海が形作ってきましたが
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='ja'>山も街の名物です
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='ja'>港のすぐ上に
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='ja'>エスカレーターで龍頭山公園の頂上へ
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='ja'>景色とともに 16 世紀
豊臣秀吉と戦った
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='ja'>李舜臣将軍像がそびえます
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='ja'>天摩山を 20 分 ほど歩くと
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='ja'>展望台がお出迎え
ダイナミックなプサンの姿が
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='ja'>目の前に広がります
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='ja'>プサン北部にある
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='ja'>5 分ほどケーブル カーを楽しむと
プサン最高峰の
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='ja'>金鋼公園に着きます
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='ja'>週末に訪れる多くの地元住民と
山を歩いてみませんか
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='ja'>遊歩道や金井山城の 
壁を散策します
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='ja'>ここは梵魚寺のお膝元でもあり
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='ja'>16 世紀と 20 世紀に
この寺の僧兵たちが
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='ja'>外敵と戦いました
<SYNC Start=360600><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=368580><P class='ja'>この英雄たちはプサンの誇りです
忠烈祠付近では
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373640><P class='ja'>1592 年にプサンを攻めた
秀吉軍との戦いに
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=378860><P class='ja'>命をかけた
民の思いを感じます
<SYNC Start=384060><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=390780><P class='ja'>1950 年にもプサンは攻撃されました
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=394640><P class='ja'>UN 記念公園には
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=397200><P class='ja'>戦死した約 14 万人の兵士が眠ります
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401900><P class='ja'>北朝鮮の兵士が押し寄せ
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=405500><P class='ja'>プサンの要塞で激戦を繰り広げました
<SYNC Start=409380><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=413340><P class='ja'>プサンは 朝鮮戦争で陥落しなかった
韓国の数少ない都市です
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=418680><P class='ja'>プサンには 50 万人を超える人々が逃れました
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=422600><P class='ja'>UN 平和記念館は
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=425400><P class='ja'>犠牲になった兵士と民間人を
ともにしのびます
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=430160><P class='ja'>今も世界で起こる争いに苦しむ
人々への思いに繋がります
<SYNC Start=435260><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=440580><P class='ja'>プサンには 当時の人々の知恵が根付き
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=444460><P class='ja'>戦後の困難から生まれた料理は
プサンの名物料理です
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=451120><P class='ja'>ある夫婦が 米兵の捨てた雑誌を
売っていた路地は
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457240><P class='ja'>書店街に姿を変えました
<SYNC Start=461140><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462740><P class='ja'>人々が日用品を交換し合った
粗末な露店は
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=467900><P class='ja'>今や韓国屈指の誰もが愛する
豊富な品ぞろえが多くを魅了する
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=472300><P class='ja'>伝統市場になりました
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=476400><P class='ja'>当時 生活を追われ プサンに逃れた人々が
港にあふれていました
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=480060><P class='ja'>それからプサンの険しい丘に
バラックが建ち並びました
<SYNC Start=486080><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486700><P class='ja'>人々がコツコツと働いて
汗水を流したこの地に時が流れ
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489960><P class='ja'>甘川村の人々が
創造性を開花させました
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=494180><P class='ja'>小道や壁はアートで彩られ
<SYNC Start=497639><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497640><P class='ja'>このエリア全体は今や知らない人はいない
注目スポットになりました
<SYNC Start=503200><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=510940><P class='ja'>甘川 のリノベーション精神は
プサンの街中にあふれる
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=515800><P class='ja'>クリエイティブで未知なることに挑む
エネルギーを象徴しています
<SYNC Start=521480><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=521479><P class='ja'>こうした熱意が世界に誇る博物館
<SYNC Start=525259><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525260><P class='ja'>ギャラリー
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=526140><P class='ja'>フェスティバルへと形を変えて街の一部を成しています
<SYNC Start=528320><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=530740><P class='ja'>ショッピングストリートや
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=534100><P class='ja'>世界的な規模を誇るデパートは
いつでも熱気にあふれています
<SYNC Start=539240><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=540380><P class='ja'>世界中の美食家をうならせる料理は
五感を使って味わってこそ
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=548420><P class='ja'>光の洪水あふれる夜景も圧巻です
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=553180><P class='ja'>年に一度のランタン フェスティバルも開催される
プサンを訪れてみませんか
<SYNC Start=558040><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=562740><P class='ja'>長きにわたる外敵との戦い
困難や苦労の果てに
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=568880><P class='ja'>このにぎやかな港町はついに
本来の姿を取り戻しました
<SYNC Start=573540><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=577280><P class='ja'>プサンは 「過去」と「未来」を格別な「今」へとつなぐ
架け橋としての役割を担っているのです
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=585140><P class='ja'>心と身体で味わい尽くす
プサンへようこそ
<SYNC Start=592920><P class='ja'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5480><P class='zh-TW'>釜山市位於
朝鮮半島東南岸
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=10600><P class='zh-TW'>從北京和東京等亞洲國家的首都
飛幾個小時就能抵達
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=14940><P class='zh-TW'>從首爾搭子彈列車出發，也只要 2.5 小時
的車程
<SYNC Start=18680><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=27400><P class='zh-TW'>釜山是韓國第一大港和第二大城
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=31100><P class='zh-TW'>沿著嶺南地方鋸齒狀的海岸線
一路延伸
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=34980><P class='zh-TW'>與內陸的群山相連
<SYNC Start=39160><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46260><P class='zh-TW'>從舊石器時代開始，就吸引先民
前來撿拾貝類的嶙峋海岸
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=51020><P class='zh-TW'>到札嘎其魚市場源源不絕的
豐富漁貨
<SYNC Start=55160><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=56540><P class='zh-TW'>…從朝鮮王朝的古老船隻
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=59540><P class='zh-TW'>到推動南韓經貿榮景的
現代化船塢
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=64080><P class='zh-TW'>釜山與海洋的關係一向密不可分
<SYNC Start=68560><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=73440><P class='zh-TW'>隨著全球邁入 21 世紀
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=77120><P class='zh-TW'>釜山也持續成長
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=79440><P class='zh-TW'>並發展成一片樂土，讓辛勤工作的韓國人
在這裡盡情放鬆
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=84040><P class='zh-TW'>重溫傳統
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=85820><P class='zh-TW'>並放眼未來
<SYNC Start=87820><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=91320><P class='zh-TW'>熙來攘往的港口是釜山
的經濟命脈
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=95540><P class='zh-TW'>不過，這裡的海灘才是吸引全亞洲旅客
趨之若鶩的魅力所在
<SYNC Start=101040><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=105200><P class='zh-TW'>從釜山車站搭地鐵只要 40 分鐘
就會來到這裡的明星景點
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110820><P class='zh-TW'>海雲臺海水浴場，也是韓國規模最大
且最受歡迎的濱海休閒勝地
<SYNC Start=117320><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=122840><P class='zh-TW'>沿著連綿不絕的沙灘往東走，就會來到
迎月之丘
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=127300><P class='zh-TW'>這裡過去是詩人吟詩歌詠
的所在
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=131280><P class='zh-TW'>現在則是咖啡愛好者鍾愛的去處
<SYNC Start=134260><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=136660><P class='zh-TW'>來到海雲臺東側
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=138840><P class='zh-TW'>不妨穿過冬柏公園，前往 APEC 世峰樓
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=142960><P class='zh-TW'>這裡是 2005 年亞太經合會期間
亞太地區的領袖齊聚一堂
<SYNC Start=148360><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=148380><P class='zh-TW'>欣賞釜山絕色美景的所在地
<SYNC Start=151860><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=159640><P class='zh-TW'>釜山的海岸線風情萬種
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=162940><P class='zh-TW'>您可以配合心情，選擇喜愛的景致或活動
<SYNC Start=166340><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=166960><P class='zh-TW'>想徹底放鬆的話
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=169140><P class='zh-TW'>前往廣安里海水浴場的半月型海灘
鋪開浴巾
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=173280><P class='zh-TW'>就能享受和緩的柔浪
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='zh-TW'>悠閒的氛圍
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='zh-TW'>和鑽石橋的美麗景致
<SYNC Start=179980><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=182200><P class='zh-TW'>想冒險的話
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=184240><P class='zh-TW'>可以前往青沙浦的漁村包船出海
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=187720><P class='zh-TW'>或是踏上龍湖洞半島
末端的天空步道
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=192720><P class='zh-TW'>欣賞一水之隔的五六島
的優美景致
<SYNC Start=196980><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=204920><P class='zh-TW'>想體驗涅槃的境界嗎？
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=206920><P class='zh-TW'>前往機張郡
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=208560><P class='zh-TW'>到歷史悠久的海東龍宮寺
許願祈福
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=212060><P class='zh-TW'>這座寺廟是韓國少數屹立於海畔的
佛寺之一
<SYNC Start=217040><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=222940><P class='zh-TW'>越過歷史悠久的影島大橋，就會來到
對岸的太宗台公園
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228440><P class='zh-TW'>根據傳說，這裡的懸崖峭壁
曾經是
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=232180><P class='zh-TW'>無數神祇和女神的歇腳處
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235580><P class='zh-TW'>新羅的第 29 代君主也曾在此彎弓射雲
度過悠閒的時光
<SYNC Start=241940><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=242880><P class='zh-TW'>對現代人來說
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=244940><P class='zh-TW'>來到這裡，欣賞貨船緩緩駛向遠方的港口
更是舒緩心情
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249480><P class='zh-TW'>放慢生活步調的好選擇
<SYNC Start=254140><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259079><P class='zh-TW'>松島海水浴場是另一個潛思冥想的好去處
<SYNC Start=263539><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=263540><P class='zh-TW'>踏上造型盤曲有如潛蛟出洞的
天空步道
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=267640><P class='zh-TW'>凌空橫渡起伏不定的
洶湧波濤
<SYNC Start=273140><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=273860><P class='zh-TW'>好好享受神遊物外的快感，小朋友也能
在多大浦海灘上盡情嬉戲
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279480><P class='zh-TW'>這裡是韓國最長河流的出海口
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=282900><P class='zh-TW'>綿延不盡的沙灘和霧氣迷濛的大海
構成海天一色的絕美勝景
<SYNC Start=288500><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290200><P class='zh-TW'>雖然釜山的發展與海洋
息息相關
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=294800><P class='zh-TW'>綿延縱伸的山脈也是當地的一大特色
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=299480><P class='zh-TW'>來到港口上方
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=300960><P class='zh-TW'>搭乘手扶梯前往龍頭山公園的山頂
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=305660><P class='zh-TW'>就能俯瞰釜山的市容，16 世紀海軍名將
李舜臣的雕像
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=310220><P class='zh-TW'>也屹立於此
<SYNC Start=313080><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=313720><P class='zh-TW'>來到鄰近的天摩山
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=315980><P class='zh-TW'>花 20 分鐘的時間登上觀景台
活力十足的釜山
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=321140><P class='zh-TW'>就能盡收眼底
<SYNC Start=323340><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=331260><P class='zh-TW'>來到市區北邊
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=332860><P class='zh-TW'>只要搭乘五分鐘的纜車
就會抵達金剛公園
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=337380><P class='zh-TW'>也是釜山最高峰的所在處
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340860><P class='zh-TW'>每週末來此登山健行的民眾
不計其數
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=344740><P class='zh-TW'>您也可以來此，深入探索 
金井山城的森林步道與城牆
<SYNC Start=349360><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=350460><P class='zh-TW'>這個公園也是梵魚寺的所在地
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=353840><P class='zh-TW'>寺內的武僧在 16 世紀和 20 世紀時
曾奮勇禦敵
<SYNC Start=357720><P class='zh-TW'>&nbsp;
