<SYNC Start=175510><P class='zh-HK'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=175510><P class='zh-HK'>輕鬆的氛圍
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='zh-HK'>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=177040><P class='zh-HK'>和廣安大橋的景致
